    "passive": {
      "name": "Rebellious Little Hawk",
      "description": "Normal attacks fire bullets with area damage and additionally deal physical damage equal to 0.5% of the target's maximum HP. When attacking on the ground, cannonballs are blocked by enemy heroes.\nI'll make it work no matter what - I'm Captain Firehawk!",
