    "skill1": {
      "name": "Upgraded Shell",
      "tags": [
        "damage"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD: 5 seconds",
      "description": "Loads enhanced shells and strengthens the next three normal attacks. Enhanced normal attacks have a larger area attack effect, dealing 180 (180 + 40% of additional physical attack) physical damage to the target and additional physical damage of 1% of the target's maximum HP.\n--The cost of the enhanced bullets created by Captain Firehawk is partially covered by the help of the indomitable mechanical arm, but unfortunately the budget is limited.",
