    "skill2": {
      "name": "Legendary Hero Debut",
      "tags": [
        "flight",
        "stealth",
        "Movement speed increase"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD: 12 seconds",
      "description": "Throw a smoke bomb and set up a smoke screen. You and your allies inside the smokescreen gain stealth for 3.5 seconds. At the same time, you will ride the explosive air current, greatly increasing your movement speed for 0.8 seconds. While in the air, you can move, attack normally, activate skills, and ignore terrain. You can extend your flight time by using normal attacks and skill 3 while in the air.\nWhen skill 2 is activated in the air, smoke bombs will not be fired, but normal attacks will not be blocked by the enemy.\n-- \"Let's surprise them!\" Firehawk's appearance was created by Captain Firehawk himself.",
      "table": {
