    "skill3": {
      "name": "Sunset Fireworks Show",
      "tags": [
        "flight",
        "super armor",
        "damage"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD: 50 seconds",
      "description": "Jump high into the air, become super armored for a certain period of time, and fire 5 missiles at each enemy hero you lock onto. Each time the missile explodes, it deals 350 (350 + 80% of additional physical attack) physical damage to enemies within range, and additional physical damage equal to 6% of the target's lost HP. If you hit the same target multiple times, the damage from the second shot onwards will be reduced to 25%. Also, an enemy hero other than the target can receive one shot instead.\n-- \"Do you want to see fireworks? Or... would you like to become a firework?\" Alessio asks.",
      "table": {
