    "status_text": "Basic status\nMax HP 3340\nMax MP 600\nPhysical attack 185 (175+10)\nMagic attack 0\nPhysical defense 150|20%\nMagic defense 75|11.1%\nattack status\nMovement speed 370\nPhysical defense penetration 0|0%\nMagic defense penetration 0|0%\nAttack speed bonus 10%\nCritical rate 0%\nCritical effect 200%\nPhysical life steal 0%\nMagic life steal 0%\nCooldown reduction 0%\nAttack range long distance\ndefense status\nResistance 0%\nHP recovery every 5 seconds 46\nMP recovery every 5 seconds 15",
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "High safety and freedom of positioning due to aerial movement",
        "Powerful AoE damage that scales depending on enemy's max HP",
        "Overwhelming carry performance in late games when equipment is available"
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Low durability in the early stages and extremely fragile until growth",
        "Weak against hard CC and high-mobility assassins who release air status.",
        "Not good at fighting in closed spaces, highly dependent on standing position"
      ],
      "playstyle": "In the early stages, focus on working with your support to safely farm and prepare your core equipment. In teamfights, always stay behind the front line and use your skills to stay in the air and deal area damage from a safe distance. The basic idea is to take advantage of its overwhelming firepower and range toward the end of the game, and use it as the main damage source in object sieges and group battles."
    },
