    "passive": {
      "name": "Fate's Guidance",
      "description": "The one who guides fate switches between long-range and close-range attacks. Skills and short-range normal attacks that hit will give you a stamp for 7 seconds.\nLong-range attack: Releases concentrated power of destiny far away, dealing 165 (100% of physical attack) physical damage and (15% of magic attack) magic damage to the enemy hit.\nClose-range attack: Attack in all directions with the divine staff, dealing 165 (100% of physical attack) physical damage and (45% of magic attack) magic damage.",
      "icon": "/images/skills/hero_109_passive.png"
    },
