      "name": "Scepter of Fate",
      "tags": [
        "damage",
        "recovery"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD: 5 seconds",
      "description": "The cooldown is reduced by 0.2 seconds each time you attack an engraving enemy. Up to 1 second.\nRanged attack: Converts the Divine Staff of Fate into energy and throws it, dealing 410 (410 + 75% of magic attack) magic damage to the enemy it hits. Furthermore, it releases an illusion of the Divine Staff of Fate at the enemy with the seal in front of it, inflicting 75% damage to the enemy.\nClose-range attack: Throws the Divine Staff of Fate while rotating, dealing 260 (260 + 45% of magic attack) magic damage to the enemy hit and reducing movement speed by 15% for 2 seconds. Recovers 150 HP (150 + 5% of additional HP) each time you attack an enemy with a stamp.\nRanged Attack: If the illusion hits the same enemy multiple times, the damage from the second hit will be 50%. Close-range attack: Can recover up to 3 times.",
      "icon": "/images/skills/hero_109_skill1.png",
