    "skill2": {
      "name": "Leap of Fate",
      "tags": [
        "move",
        "recovery",
        "conversion"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD: 6 seconds",
      "description": "Moves forward and attacks at long range if there are no enemy heroes nearby, or at close range if there are enemy heroes nearby.\nRanged Attack: Increases movement speed by 15% for 2 seconds. Skill effectiveness increases by 25% (up to 50%) for each enemy hero at the starting point of the charge. Activating Skill 2 switches from short-range attacks to long-range attacks, increasing movement speed and doubling the upper limit.\nClose-range attack: Max HP and Max MP increase by 100, recover 450 (450 + 12% of additional HP) HP, and increase Max HP by the same amount. For each enemy hero near the end of the charge, the Guide of Destiny's healing effect increases by 25% (up to a maximum of 50%). When you activate Skill 2 and switch from long-range attacks to short-range attacks, the additional recovery effect and upper limit will be doubled.",
      "icon": "/images/skills/hero_109_skill2.png",
      "table": {
        "headers": [
