        "description": "Releases a phantom butterfly in a fan-shaped area and strengthens passive skills for 2 seconds. The butterfly deals 400 (400 + 72% of magic attack power) magic damage to enemies within range and reduces enemy movement speed by 30% for 2 seconds.",
