          "Movement speed increase"
        ],
        "cooldown_text": "",
        "description": "Deals 250 (250 + 30% of magic attack power) magic damage to nearby enemies and applies 1 stack of engraving, and each stack deals 125 (125 + 15% of magic attack power) magic damage to the target for 5 seconds. Maximum 5 stacks.\nAt the same time, give 1 stack of Imprint to yourself and nearby friendly heroes, and each stack increases the target's movement speed by 3%. Maximum of 5 stacks, duration is 5 seconds.\nPassive effect: Activates skill 2 once every 7 seconds.",
