    "hero_id": "113",
    "hero_name": "Devara",
    "passive": {
      "name": "Passive: Wish of the Living",
      "description": "Normal attacks at close range have shorter attack intervals.\nGain 1 power of sentient beings for each normal attack (up to 6), and when the maximum is reached, you can activate Tenrai and activate an additional basic skill.\nActivating the basic skill strengthens your normal attack, deals an additional 85 (85 + 35% of physical attack) magic damage to enemies within range, and recovers 75 (75 + 1.2% of additional HP) HP.\nLong-range enhanced normal attacks deal 75% damage to units other than the target. (No special effects occur)",
      "table": {
