    "skill2": {
      "name": "Skill 2: Divine Judgment",
      "description": "Releases the power of lightning in front of you. If you reach the maximum distance/contact a unit, it will explode after a certain period of time, dealing 200 (200 + 45% of physical attack) magic damage and knocking it back.\nThe closer you are to the unit, the greater the knockback distance.",
      "table": {
        "headers": [
          "Lv.1",
          "Lv.2",
          "Lv.3",
          "Lv.4",
          "Lv.5",
          "Lv.6"
        ],
        "rows": [
          {
            "label": "Basic damage",
            "values": [
              "200",
              "240",
              "280",
              "320",
              "360",
              "400"
            ]
          },
          {
            "label": "cool down",
            "values": [
              "8",
              "7.7",
              "7.4",
              "7.1",
              "6.8",
              "6.5"
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "skill3": {
      "name": "Skill 3: Millennium Echo",
      "description": "Resonating with the reverberations of a thousand years, it floats in the air and enters the lightning body inheritance state.\nDuring the 1.5 second status change, you gain super armor status, increasing your movement speed by 30% and ignoring terrain. In addition, Vajra uses Vajra to randomly strike nearby enemies (hero priority), dealing 100 (100 + 22% of physical attack) magic damage, gaining 1 sentient power, and gaining 160 (160 + 2.5% of additional HP) shield for 2 seconds. After landing, deals 200 (200 + 45% of physical attack) magic damage to nearby enemies.\nThe transformed state lasts for 8 seconds. During this time, the range of enhanced normal attacks increases, and normal attacks gain 2 sentient powers. Long-range normal attacks have a chain bolt effect that bounces between multiple enemies, dealing 86 (50% of physical attack) physical damage.",
      "table": {
        "headers": [
          "Lv.1",
          "Lv.2",
          "Lv.3"
        ],
        "rows": [
          {
            "label": "cool down",
            "values": [
              "60",
              "54",
              "48"
            ]
          },
          {
            "label": "lightning damage",
            "values": [
              "100",
              "150",
              "200"
            ]
          },
          {
            "label": "Landing damage",
            "values": [
              "200",
              "300",
              "400"
            ]
          },
          {
            "label": "shield every time",
            "values": [
              "160",
              "240",
              "320"
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "He has a high self-healing ability due to his passive, and the amount of healing from minions and monsters does not decrease, so his lane maintenance ability is extremely high.",
        "By combining skills and enhanced normal attacks, it boasts high mobility that allows it to quickly approach the enemy's rear guard."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Operations such as passive \"power of sentient beings\" gauge management and skill combo judgment are highly difficult and require proficiency.",
        "Due to its nature of rushing in like an assassin, it is vulnerable to CC (control) when deep inside enemy lines, and is easily defeated by concentrated attacks."
      ],
      "playstyle": "Mainly used in crash lanes and jungles. In the early stages, take advantage of the passive recovery effect (even minions don't attenuate) and trade damage aggressively while maintaining an HP advantage. In group battles, instead of charging head-on, you stand by with your passive gauge filling up, and use combos like ``Skill 1 → Enhanced Normal Attack'' to quickly close the distance on enemy marksmen and mages and unleash instant firepower."
    }
  },
  "hero_173": {
    "lore": "",
    "skills": [
      {
        "id": "P",
        "name": "パッシブスキル：密偵の耳",
        "tags": [
          "視界",
          "ダメージ"
        ],
        "cooldown_text": "",
        "description": "盗聴により敵ヒーローの痕跡を把握し、敵の視界を1秒獲得する（同一のユニットには6秒に1回発動）。\nまた、モンスターの弱点を見破ることができ、全ての攻撃でモンスターに追加で7.5~15%の物理ダメージを与える。",
        "table": null
      },
      {
        "id": "skill1",
        "name": "スキル1：潜入作戦",
        "tags": [
          "ダメージ",
          "強化",
          "刻印"
        ],
        "cooldown_text": "",
        "description": "通常攻撃時にターゲットに闇の刻印を1スタック付与する（最大4スタックまで）。4秒後に爆発し、範囲内の敵に230（230+追加物理攻撃の75%）の物理ダメージを与える。刻印1スタックごとに爆発時に追加で230（230+追加物理攻撃の75%）の物理ダメージを与え、4スタックに達すると即座に爆発する。\nスキルを発動すると4秒間攻撃速度が35%、攻撃範囲が75増加する。",
        "table": null
      },
      {
        "id": "skill2",
        "name": "スキル2：刃遁",
        "tags": [
          "移動",
          "無効化",
          "移動速度減少"
        ],
        "cooldown_text": "",
        "description": "指定方向にチャクラムを投げ、幻影のような身のこなしで到達地点まで移動してキャッチする（移動中はターゲット不可状態）。チャクラムは敵に260（260+追加物理攻撃の80%）の物理ダメージを与え、2秒間移動速度を15%減少させる。王都の密偵が通過した後の地面は2.9秒間燃焼し続け、ルート上の敵に0.25秒ごとに110（110+追加物理攻撃の30%）の物理ダメージを与え、移動速度を15%減少させる。",
        "table": null
      },
      {
        "id": "skill3",
        "name": "スキル3：無限の竜巻",
        "tags": [
          "ダメージ",
          "移動速度減少"
        ],
        "cooldown_text": "",
        "description": "指定位置にチャクラムを投げ、チャクラムの回転で引き起こした竜巻の範囲内の敵に320（320+追加物理攻撃の100%）の物理ダメージを与える。竜巻は5.4秒間、範囲内の敵に0.5秒ごとに140（140+追加物理攻撃の40%）の物理ダメージを与え、移動速度を50%減少させる。\n竜巻の内側にいる敵へのダメージは2倍となる。竜巻によるダメージでも闇の刻印をスタックできる。",
        "table": null
      }
    ]
  },
