      {
        "id": "skill1",
        "name": "Deadly Fang",
        "tags": [
          "over the wall",
          "Movement speed increase",
          "reinforcement"
        ],
        "cooldown_text": "",
        "description": "Summons one Engetsuto and increases own movement speed by 45% (decreases over 2 seconds). Engetsuto slashes the target continuously for 6 seconds when attacking, dealing 74 (40 + 20% of physical attack) physical damage each time. While the skill is active, you can jump over walls. The cutting speed of the Engetsuto increases by up to 25% depending on the level.",
        "table": null
      },
      {
        "id": "skill2",
        "name": "Furtive Attack",
        "tags": [
          "damage",
          "Movement speed decreased"
        ],
        "cooldown_text": "",
        "description": "Summons Fire Snake to the specified location. After a certain period of time, Firesnake will charge towards itself, dealing 320 (320 + 80% of additional physical attack) magic damage to enemies along its path and reducing their movement speed by 25% for 2 seconds.\nIf Firesnake owns the Engetsuto, the enemy hit by the Firesnake will be cut by the Engetsuto.\nIf Firesnake does not own the Engetsuto, the CD of Skill 2 will be reduced by 50%.\nThe activation motion of this skill becomes shorter as the attack speed increases.",
        "table": null
      },
      {
        "id": "skill3",
        "name": "Blazing Glare",
        "tags": [
          "blindness",
          "CC",
          "reinforcement"
        ],
        "cooldown_text": "",
        "description": "Fires a fire snake in the specified direction, dealing 480 (480 + 120% of additional physical attack) magic damage to enemies along the route and inflicting blindness for 2 seconds.\nImmediately summons one Engetsuto and strengthens itself for 6 seconds. During the enhancement period, energy is accumulated when attacking or being attacked by an enemy, and each time energy reaches the upper limit, it deals 240 (240 + 60% of additional physical attack) magic damage to enemies within range and knocks them up for 0.5 seconds.\nEnemies affected by the blinding effect can no longer be damaged by normal attacks, and projectiles when activating skills will randomly deviate from the target.",
        "table": null
      }
    ],
