    "status_text": "Basic status\nMax HP 3409\nMax MP 0\nPhysical attack 182 (172+10)\nMagic attack 0\nPhysical defense 150|20%\nMagic defense 75|11.1%\nattack status\nMovement speed 380\nPhysical defense penetration 0|0%\nMagic defense penetration 0|0%\nAttack speed bonus 5%\nCritical rate 0%\nCritical effect 200%\nPhysical life steal 0%\nMagic life steal 0%\nCooldown reduction 0%\nAttack range close range\ndefense status\nResistance 0%\nHP recovery every 5 seconds 49\nMP recovery every 5 seconds 0",
    "passive": {
      "name": "Slack Off a Lil Bit",
      "description": "Since energy (fist and leg strength) is consumed when a skill is activated, if you let your guard down a little, you will sit down and become lazy. When you are lazy, your energy recovery speed increases by 25%, and you can eat various snacks to randomly recover 1x/1.5x/2x HP of 110 (110 + 2% of additional HP).\nThe effect is interrupted when attacking, being attacked, and while moving. Don't be lazy while in serious mode.\nAfter activating a combo move, if you use a different combo move within 3 seconds, the effect will increase by 25%.",
      "icon": "/images/skills/hero_110_passive.png"
    },
    "skill1": {
      "name": "Whatever (I)",
      "tags": [
        "damage",
        "CC",
        "move"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD: 0 seconds",
      "description": "Dash in the specified direction. If there are enemies in front of you, pull them in front of you, deal 300 (300 + 100% of additional physical attack) physical damage to targets in a fan-shaped area in front of you, and reduce movement speed by 30% for 1 second.\nCountermeasures against the weak: Immediately after the skill is activated, if you activate \"Appropriate Type - Part 1\" again, you will jump up and deliver a powerful blow, dealing 400 (400 + 125% of additional physical attack) physical damage + up to 10% of the target's current maximum HP physical damage to enemies within the range, knocking them up for 1 second. (Enemies in the center of the area will receive an additional 50% damage)\nWhile the skill is active, damage taken is reduced by 25%.\nForward or backward: If you activate \"Appropriate Type - Part 2\" immediately after using the skill, you will perform a striking combo of kicks and punches. First punch 3 times, each punch dealing 200 (200 + 70% of additional physical attack) physical damage, and finally knee kick, dealing 200 (200 + 70% of additional physical attack) physical damage and slightly knocking back (no CC). At the same time, recovers 200 HP (200 + 5% of additional maximum HP).\nThis skill consumes 1 gauge of fist power. Fist power regenerates 1 gauge every 8.5 seconds (up to 2 gauge, depending on cooldown reduction).",
      "icon": "/images/skills/hero_110_skill1.png",
      "forms": [
        {
          "form_name": "Whatever (I)",
          "description": "Dash in the specified direction. If there are enemies in front of you, pull them in front of you, deal 300 (300 + 100% of additional physical attack) physical damage to targets in a fan-shaped area in front of you, and reduce movement speed by 30% for 1 second.\nCountermeasures against the weak: Immediately after the skill is activated, if you activate \"Appropriate Type - Part 1\" again, you will jump up and deliver a powerful blow, dealing 400 (400 + 125% of additional physical attack) physical damage + up to 10% of the target's current maximum HP physical damage to enemies within the range, knocking them up for 1 second. (Enemies in the center of the area will receive an additional 50% damage)\nWhile the skill is active, damage taken is reduced by 25%.\nForward or backward: If you activate \"Appropriate Type - Part 2\" immediately after using the skill, you will perform a striking combo of kicks and punches. First punch 3 times, each punch dealing 200 (200 + 70% of additional physical attack) physical damage, and finally knee kick, dealing 200 (200 + 70% of additional physical attack) physical damage and slightly knocking back (no CC). At the same time, recovers 200 HP (200 + 5% of additional maximum HP).\nThis skill consumes 1 gauge of fist power. Fist power regenerates 1 gauge every 8.5 seconds (up to 2 gauge, depending on cooldown reduction).",
