    "skill2": {
      "name": "Whatever (II)",
      "tags": [
        "super armor",
        "Damage reduction",
        "move"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD: 0 seconds",
      "description": "Cartwheel forward and dodge enemy attacks. While active, you gain super armor status, reducing damage taken by 30% and recovering 200 HP (200 + 5% of additional maximum HP).\nCountermeasures against strong people: If you activate ``Appropriate Type Part 2'' again immediately after activating the skill, you will launch a flying kick towards the enemy, dealing 500 (500 + 150% of additional physical attack) physical damage, recovering 200 HP (200 + 5% of additional maximum HP), and using the recoil to jump into the air. While activated, you gain super armor status, reducing damage taken by 25% and recovering 300 HP (300 + 5% of additional maximum HP).\nAttack is the best defense: If you activate \"Appropriate Type - Part 1\" immediately after activating the skill, you will teleport behind the enemy and deliver a roundhouse kick, knocking them back and dealing 350 (350 + 110% of additional physical attack) physical damage, and additionally dealing physical damage equal to 15% of the maximum HP the target is missing. When you defeat an enemy, recover 300 HP (300 + 5% of additional maximum HP) and 50% energy (doubled when defeating an enemy hero).\nThis skill consumes 1 gauge of leg strength. Leg strength recovers 1 gauge every 8.5 seconds (up to 2 gauge, depending on cooldown reduction).",
