    "skill3": {
      "name": "Get Serious",
      "tags": [
        "reinforcement",
        "Movement speed increase",
        "damage"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD: 60 seconds",
      "description": "Enters magic mode and deals 360 (360 + 100% of additional physical attack) physical damage to nearby enemies.\nWhen you enter Magi Mode, you will immediately recover 1 gauge of fist power and leg strength, and the maximum energy stack will be 3 gauges. While active, movement speed increases by 15% and reduces movement speed reduction effects by 50%. This state lasts for 10 seconds.",
      "icon": "/images/skills/hero_110_skill3.png"
    },
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Powerful group battle initiation ability that can create a starting point for allies",
        "Lockdown performance that reliably takes down priority targets (mages and marksmen)",
        "Excellent survival ability utilizing high mobility and skills"
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "It requires an understanding of various skill combos and is extremely difficult to operate.",
        "If you jump in at the wrong time, you will be isolated in the enemy camp and easily defeated.",
        "It depends on the accuracy of the skill, and there is a high risk if you miss."
      ],
      "playstyle": "As a fighter or jungler, fight using complex skill combos depending on the situation. In group battles, he will not miss the moment when the enemy's CC runs out or the formation collapses, and will jump into the enemy's back line and instantly kill soft carries. It is important to be conscious of hit and away, take advantage of your high mobility, and run freely around the battlefield while racking up reliable kills."
    },
    "meta": {
      "summoner_spells": [
        "epiphany",
        "weakening"
