      "cooldown": "CD: 18 seconds",
      "description": "Jumps towards the specified target and deals 557 (400 + 90% of additional physical attack) physical damage (if the target is marked, deals additional true damage of 12% of lost HP). For 4 seconds after hitting the target, reduce normal attack damage by 50% and imprint the target for an additional 4 seconds.\nRecovers HP equal to 35% of the damage dealt while applying the stamp. If the target is defeated, the CD of the secret technique will be reset.\nWhen a normal attack hits a unit with an imprint, the cooldown of skills 1 and 2 is reduced by 1 second.",
