    "status_text": "Basic status\nMax HP 3400\nMax MP 0\nPhysical attack 185 (175+10)\nMagic attack 0\nPhysical defense 150|20%\nMagic defense 75|11.1%\nattack status\nMovement speed 380\nPhysical defense penetration 0|0%\nMagic defense penetration 0|0%\nAttack speed bonus 0%\nCritical rate 0%\nCritical effect 200%\nPhysical life steal 0%\nMagic life steal 0%\nCooldown reduction 0%\nAttack range close range\ndefense status\nResistance 0%\nHP recovery every 5 seconds 57\nMP recovery every 5 seconds 0",
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Overwhelming continuous kill performance where skills are reset with kills and assists",
        "Powerful burst damage that instantly defeats soft targets",
        "Jungle rotation speed is fast, making it easy to put pressure on the entire map"
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "He is not good at starting group battles on his own and relies on the engagement ability of his allies.",
        "Extremely weak to CC (movement interference), and if caught you will be defeated without being able to do anything.",
        "If you can't get a kill and don't activate the reset, there will be no escape route and the risk of death will increase."
      ],
      "playstyle": "As a jungle assassin, farm quickly from the beginning, and from level 4 onwards, actively gank and aim for snowballs. Never enter first in teamfights, and wait until your allies have whittled down the enemy's health and the enemy's main CC skills have been used up. The basic idea is to reliably take down targets with reduced physical strength and use passive skill resets to clean up the battlefield one after another."
    },
    "meta": {
      "summoner_spells": [
        "punishment"
      ],
      "synergy": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Zhuangzhou",
          "reason": "Because it can give CC immunity and damage reduction, and you can aim for a chain of kill recovery without being hindered.",
          "hero_id": "hero_015"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Sumiko",
          "reason": "This is because you can stop the enemy with a long-range stun, creating an opening for Butterfly to safely jump in.",
          "hero_id": "hero_013"
        }
      ],
      "counters": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Lu Bu",
          "reason": "Because it has range CC and high durability, and can break the chain of Butterfly's skill reset.",
          "hero_id": "hero_024"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Diao cicada",
          "reason": "This is because you can use your invincibility judgment and recovery to avoid Butterfly's burst damage while also counterattacking it.",
          "hero_id": "hero_040"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "hero_142": {
    "lore": "",
    "skills": [
      {
        "id": "P",
        "name": "フレイム・スペル",
        "tags": [],
        "cooldown_text": "",
        "description": "アクティブスキルが命中した敵に燃焼効果を毎回1スタック付与し、自身は移動速度増加を1スタック獲得する。それぞれ最大10スタックまで獲得可能。持続時間は3秒。\n燃焼効果1スタックごとに、アクティブスキルのダメージ発生時に追加で10（10+魔法攻撃力の2%）の魔法ダメージを与える。\n加速効果1スタックごとに自身の移動速度が2%増加する。",
        "table": null
      },
      {
        "id": "skill1",
        "name": "ファイアボール",
        "tags": [
          "ダメージ"
        ],
        "cooldown_text": "",
        "description": "指定方向に5つのファイアボールを放つ。各ファイアボールは敵ヒーローに命中すると、280（280+魔法攻撃力の30%）の魔法ダメージを与えて消失する。また、ルート上にいる非ヒーローユニットにも同等のダメージを与える。\n複数のファイアボールが同じ敵ヒーローに命中した場合、2つ目以降のダメージは30%となる。",
        "table": null
      },
      {
        "id": "skill2",
        "name": "カオス・フレイム",
        "tags": [
          "CC",
          "移動速度減少",
          "ダメージ"
        ],
        "cooldown_text": "",
        "description": "指定方向にカオス・フレイムを放つ。炎が敵に命中、もしくは最長距離に到達すると炎渦に変化し、最初に命中した敵を1秒間スタンさせる。\n炎渦が持続している間、0.5秒ごとに付近の敵に125（125+魔法攻撃力の20%）の魔法ダメージを与え、移動速度を1.5秒間30%減少させる。",
        "table": null
      },
      {
        "id": "skill3",
        "name": "スコーチングビーム",
        "tags": [
          "ダメージ",
          "スーパーアーマー",
          "シールド"
        ],
        "cooldown_text": "",
        "description": "指定方向にスコーチングビームを発射する。発射中は方向を調整でき、ルート上の敵に150（150+魔法攻撃力の21%）の魔法ダメージを最大で12回与える。\nスコーチングビームを発射すると、850（850+魔法攻撃力の88%）のシールドを獲得し、シールドが存在している間、スーパーアーマー効果を獲得する。\n発動から0.5秒経過後、スキルを再発動することでキャンセルできる。",
        "table": null
      }
    ]
  },
