    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Excellent initiation ability with strong AoE knockup and terrain generation",
        "Amazing sustain (durability) that converts received damage into recovery",
        "Stable combat due to CC invalidation effect while using skills"
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Poor firepower in the early stages and tends to rely on follow-up from allies for kills",
        "It is difficult to apply skills to enemies with high mobility and they are likely to be kited.",
        "If you buy an item that inhibits recovery, your durability will decrease significantly."
      ],
      "playstyle": "He is in charge of the crash lane and specializes in destroying enemy formations as a solid front line for his allies. It is effective to fight in the jungle or in narrow terrain around objects, and use your ultimate to generate walls and cut off the enemy's escape route. By making full use of the recovery power of his passive and the CC immunity of his skill, he collects enemy hate and creates an environment where it is easy for his allies to deal damage."
    },
