    "passive": {
      "name": "Whirling Featherblades",
      "description": "If the target is far away, use a normal attack to throw a rotating flying blade. The next long-range attack cannot be performed until the flying blade is returned to hand. If you tap a normal attack just before the flying blade returns, you can quickly move forward, bounce the flying blade, and attack again. Damage increases by 1.5 for every 1% of attack speed, and damage and flying speed of flying blade increase by 5% for each bounce (up to 3 times).\nIf the target is close, it enters close-range combat mode and quickly attacks the enemy 3 times, dealing physical damage equal to 110% of the total physical attack.\nStacks a stamp on the target with each normal attack, and deals additional damage according to the number of stacks when \"Feather Storm\" hits.",
      "icon": "/images/skills/hero_108_passive.png"
    },
