      "description": "Charges forward, knocking back (no CC) enemies on the route, and dealing 150 + 50% of additional physical attack physical damage to enemies on the route. At the same time, activates the \"Zanbai Seal\" on all enemies hit, and spreads the stamp to nearby enemies.\nIf there is an enemy within range in front of you, attack with flying blades 8 times in a row while dancing gracefully. Deals physical damage equal to 110 + 38% of additional physical attack and recovers own HP by 45 + 0.8% of additional HP (recovery amount is halved if it hits a non-hero unit). If in the unyielding state, the last attack deals 100% additional damage. Each hit consumes 1 stack of the target's engraving and deals an additional 40 + 15% of additional physical attack physical damage.\nYou can move while dancing, and you can cancel this skill by reactivating it. If the dance is not activated, the cooldown will be reduced to 60%.",
