      "description": "Restores Togun's glory, deals 400 + 140% of additional physical damage to nearby enemies, and temporarily increases HP by 50% and movement speed by 50% (decreases continuously). The unyielding state lasts for 4 seconds, and the recovery effect during that time will be reflected when the unyielding state ends.\nIf you die while Skill 3 is not on cooldown, you will be revived after a certain period of time and will go on cooldown after dealing 400 + 140% of additional physical attack physical damage to nearby enemies.\nPassive: Leveling up this skill increases the number of attacks of Feather Storm by 2 and the number of attacks of melee normal attacks by 1, and each additional normal attack deals 50 physical damage.\nIf you lose all of this temporary HP, the indomitable state ends immediately. Also, the temporary HP gained when resurrecting from death will be 50% of the normal activation.",
