    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "High mobility and engagement ability to quickly jump into the enemy's rearguard",
        "Jungle laps are fast, making it easy to control the tempo of the match from the beginning.",
        "Flexible and continuous combat power through continuous use of skills"
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "It is weak to hard CC (movement interference) and can be easily defeated if caught.",
        "Passive management and skill combos are complex and difficult to operate.",
        "In the final stages of the battle, where the scale of group battles increases, it is difficult to generate firepower and the game tends to stall."
      ],
      "playstyle": "As a jungler, you can actively gank from the beginning and control the tempo of the match to create an advantage. In group battles, instead of charging head-on, wait until the enemy's main CC skills are used up before targeting the isolated, soft backline. It requires a fighting style that disrupts the battlefield by accumulating cooldown reduction, constantly using skills, and repeating hit and away."
    },
