      "description": "Strengthens the next normal attack every 7.5 seconds to 6 seconds (reduced depending on hero level). Move in front of the enemy with a swing, deal 379 (210 + 100% of magic attack + 30% of maximum HP) magic damage, knock them back, and use the momentum to jump backwards.\nWhen an ally hero receives the effect of \"Blessing of Good Matches\" (allies with full HP are not eligible for the gold bonus; if used on an ally with 50% or more HP, the bonus is halved) or an enemy hero receives the effect of \"Peace of Bad Matches\", you will receive 20 gold as a bonus, and the cooldown of enhanced normal attacks will be reduced by 50%.",
