      "cooldown": "CD: 12.5 seconds",
      "description": "Pray for a good match for an ally hero and recover 200 HP (200 + 30% of magic attack). If heroes with \"Good Match\" come close to each other within 5 seconds, their movement speed will be increased by 30%, and \"Blessing of Good Match\" will be activated when they get within a certain distance. When doing so, each hero recovers 400 HP (400 + 60% of magic attack) and increases movement speed for 2 seconds.\nIf you activate it again against an ally who has already been given \"Good Match\", it will move towards the target and activate \"Blessing of Good Match\", recovering 400 HP (400 + 60% of magic attack) for 2 seconds and increasing movement speed by 30%. He also recovers 400 HP (400 + 60% of magic attack + 8% of additional HP).\nYou can activate this skill again within 5 seconds, or the cooldown will be reset.",
