        "Dash"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD: 12.5 seconds",
      "description": "Warns enemy heroes of a \"bad relationship\", inflicts stealth immunity for 5 seconds, deals 45 (45 + 6% of magic attack) magic damage per second, and collects 2x gold (does not apply to non-hero units). Deals 225 (225 + 30% of magic attack) magic damage when the effect ends. When heroes who have been warned of \"bad connections\" come close to each other, their movement speed is reduced by 25%, and when they get within a certain distance, \"harmony\" is activated. When ``Peace of Evil'' is activated, damage to the enemy will be interrupted and the collected gold will be returned within 5 seconds.\nIf activated again against an enemy hero who has already been warned of \"Bad Relationships\", he moves towards the target and activates \"Peace of Bad Relationships\", snares the target for 0.75 seconds, dealing a total of 600 (600 + 80% of magic attack) magic damage (the magic damage of \"Peace of Bad Relationships\" is immediately settled). During this time, the damage received by the Wish Spinner is reduced by 25% (double the damage received from the target).\nThe collected gold is temporarily stored, and when the target defeats/assists the Wish Spinner, 100%/50% of it is returned.\nYou can activate this skill again within 5 seconds, or the cooldown will be reset.",
