    "status_text": "Basic Attributes\nMax HP 3332\nMax Mana 620\nPhysical Attack 169\nMagical Attack 10 (0+10)\nPhysical Defense 150|20%\nMagical Defense 75|11.1%\nAttack Attributes\nMovement Speed 365\nPhysical Defense貫通 0|0%\nMagical Defense貫通 0|0%\nAttack Speed Bonus 5%\nCritical Rate 0%\nCritical Damage 200%\nPhysical Lifesteal 0%\nMagical Lifesteal 0%\nCooldown Reduction 0%\nAttack Range Ranged\nDefense Attributes\nResistance 0%\nHP Regen/5s 45\nMana Regen/5s 15",
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Unique economic manipulation ability to steal enemy gold and return it to allies",
        "Powerful support for allies through continuous recovery and buffing",
        "CC controls the battle situation, such as movement obstruction and positional control."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Unique operations and high judgment are required, such as double casting of skills and gold management.",
        "Has low durability and is easily killed by enemy assassins if you stand in the wrong position.",
        "It has no fighting power on its own and relies heavily on the cooperation and follow-up of its allies."
      ],
      "playstyle": "As a support player, you will increase the firepower of your allies while taking gold from enemy carries to expand your team's economic advantage. Use the additional effect activated by pressing the skill twice at the right time to block the enemy's movement and gain an advantage in battle. Your biggest role is to always maintain a safe position near your allies and keep applying heals and buffs while assessing the battle situation."
    },
