      "name": "Flow of the World",
      "description": "By taking ``flow'' into your body at the base, you can choose one of the following four types to strengthen it.\nVitality: Maximum HP increases by 300, physical and magic defense increases by 50.\nPenetration: Increases maximum HP by 300 and physical attack by 30.\nSwift: Max HP increases by 300 and movement speed increases by 3.5%.\nFocus: Max HP is 300 and cooldown is reduced by 5%.\nConsumes 1 stack of \"Flow\" to strengthen normal attacks. Enhanced normal attack deals 408 (220 + 100% of physical attack + 4% of additional HP) physical damage to the enemy and restores 125 (125 + 2.5% of additional HP) HP.",
