      "description": "Charges at the target, knocking back enemies in its path, and slashes forward, dealing 600 (600 + 185% of additional physical attack) physical damage and gaining 350 (350 + 7% of additional HP) shield for 3 seconds.\nIf used consecutively against the same target within 1.5 seconds, the effects will change in the following order.\n\"Repel Cloud Type\": Deals the same amount of slash damage to enemies, knocks them up for 0.33 seconds, and gains the same amount of shield.\n\"Rear Type\": Deals the same amount of slash damage to enemies, knocks them up for 0.66 seconds, and gains the same amount of shield.\nIf activated by consuming 4 stacks of \"Flow\", it will not go on cooldown (except during skill cooldown).\nAll units other than heroes within range also receive the same CC effect as heroes.",
