      "playstyle": "When operating as a mage, the basics are long-range attacks from the rear and skill rotation that takes into account the stacking of \"flow\". Deal damage with skills while keeping your distance from the enemy, and unleash your firepower based on the opportunities created by your allies' vanguard. It is necessary to appropriately select passive strengthening effects (magic attacks and penetration power) depending on the situation and maximize damage efficiency."
