    "status_text": "Attributes\nBasic Attributes\nMax HP 3213\nMax Mana 640\nPhysical Attack 168\nMagical Attack 10 (0+10)\nPhysical Defense 150|20%\nMagical Defense 75|11.1%\nAttack Attributes\nMovement Speed 365\nPhysical Defense貫通 0|0%\nMagical Defense貫通 0|0%\nAttack Speed Bonus 5%\nCritical Rate 0%\nCritical Damage 200%\nPhysical Lifesteal 0%\nMagical Lifesteal 0%\nCooldown Reduction 0%\nAttack Range Ranged\nDefense Attributes\nResistance 0%\nHP Regen/5s 45\nMana Regen/5s 16",
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Overwhelming lane/tower push power using robots (minions)",
        "Control ability that applies pressure from the beginning and keeps opponents in the lane."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Low mobility and very vulnerable to Assassin ganks and close quarters combat.",
        "Against heroes who can quickly deal with robots, it is easy to completely block their strengths."
      ],
      "playstyle": "The basic strategy is to stay in a safe position at the back and leave the summoned robots to push lanes and scrape towers. Deploy robots aggressively from the beginning to push enemy mid laners under the tower and take control of the map. In group battles, aim for a burst by hitting important targets with Ult's stun, but you must pay close attention to where you stand as you have no self-defense skills."
    },
    "meta": {
      "summoner_spells": [
        "Flash"
      ],
      "synergy": [
