        "Her passive grants movement speed upon hitting enemies, making it easy to kite and reposition."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Low durability, making her extremely vulnerable to assassin burst damage and unexpected engages.",
        "Her damage and survivability rely heavily on landing skill shots. If she misses Skill 2 knock-up, she is highly susceptible to counterattacks."
      ],
      "playstyle": "Use Skill 1 to chip away at enemy health from a safe distance, leveraging the passive movement speed boost to perform hit-and-run tactics. In team fights, cast your ultimate from behind your frontline to deal area damage, and use Skill 2 to knock up approaching enemies for self-defense or securing kills."
