    "status_text": "Sun Shangxiang Sonshouko Heavy Artillery Princess Adjustment Apprentice Marksman 0/100 Marksman Heavy Artillery Marksman Charge/Kill Endgame Difficulty: Hard",
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Overwhelming burst damage and scaling that can melt even the enemy's vanguard in the final stages of the game.",
        "High mobility due to skill 1's rolling and the ability to kite while avoiding enemy skills."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Their combat power is low in the early stages, and they tend to lack firepower until they have the equipment.",
        "Due to its low durability, if you stand in the wrong position or receive CC, you will be defeated in an instant."
      ],
      "playstyle": "In the early stages, work together with Support to farm safely and complete core items quickly. The basic idea is to use Skill 1 to adjust your position and continue hitting with enhanced normal attacks to constantly provide firepower and shorten the cooldown of Skill 1. Always keep a safe distance in group battles, use Skill 2 to lower the enemy's defenses, and then immediately shoot at the rear guard or important targets."
    },
    "meta": {
      "summoner_spells": [
        "epiphany"
      ],
      "synergy": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Lian Po",
          "reason": "This is because she can restrain the enemy with strong CC and create an opening for her to inflict burst damage from a safe position.",
          "hero_id": "hero_004"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Lu Bu",
          "reason": "This is because she can force group battles with a wide range of launches and create an environment where she can move freely and defeat enemies individually.",
          "hero_id": "hero_024"
        }
      ],
      "counters": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Donghuang",
          "reason": "This is because her mobility will be completely nullified with a guaranteed hard CC, and she will be defeated without giving her a chance to escape.",
          "hero_id": "hero_071"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Mozi",
          "reason": "This is because you can use a long-range stun to stop her movement and prevent her from hitting and away, which is her specialty.",
          "hero_id": "hero_013"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "hero_015": {
    "hero_id": "015",
    "hero_name": "Chuangzi",
    "hero_title": "dreamy sage",
    "role": "Support",
    "sub_role": "Support/Tank",
    "difficulty": "easy",
    "stats": {
      "survival": 8,
      "attack": 3,
      "skill": 4,
      "difficulty": 2
    },
    "status_text": "Zhuangzi Sou Dream Sage Apprentice Support 0/100 Support/Tank Guardian Support Team Buff Late Stage Difficulty: Easy",
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "A powerful anti-CC ability that can release all allies from CC (incapacitated) state.",
        "Excellent survivability due to high damage reduction rate and mobility, and sustained damage output."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Since it does not have hard CC (stun, etc.) that can definitely capture the enemy, it is difficult to initiate battles on its own.",
        "If the enemy team doesn't have a lot of CC or has a lot of percentage damage, it's easy to get corrupted."
      ],
      "playstyle": "It is very good as a counter pick against enemy compositions with strong CC skills. In group battles, you collect attacks and hate from enemies on the front lines, and at the moment your allies receive fatal CC, you activate your ultimate and rescue them. Instead of taking kills yourself, you need to always know the location of your allies and support the entire team by removing debuffs and reducing damage."
    },
    "meta": {
      "summoner_spells": [
        "epiphany",
        "execution"
      ],
      "synergy": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Lady Sun",
          "reason": "By releasing CC, we can continue to take advantage of her mobility and safely deliver continuous high firepower.",
          "hero_id": "hero_014"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Marco Polo",
          "reason": "By removing the enemy's CC while his ULT is active, he can deal fatal area damage without interruption.",
          "hero_id": "hero_033"
        }
      ],
      "counters": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Pei Qinhu",
          "reason": "Because it doesn't rely on CC and attacks with overwhelming burst damage, the strength of CC removal cannot be utilized.",
          "hero_id": "hero_083"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Mozi",
          "reason": "This is because continuous pokes and stuns from a distance will keep them from getting close, creating a situation where you have no choice but to use ULT.",
          "hero_id": "hero_013"
        }
      ]
    },
    "passive": {
      "name": "Passive Skill: Natural Will",
      "description": "[Tag] Purify, damage reduction, movement speed increase\nEvery 6 seconds, enters the \"dream realm\" for 2 seconds and recovers 40 HP (40 + 0.6% of additional HP). \"Dream Realm\": Removes CC from self and strengthens self for 2 seconds. While enhanced, all CC will be nullified, damage taken will be reduced by 15%, and movement speed will be increased by 15%.\n[HP recovery] Lv.1: 40 / Lv.15: 80"
    },
    "skill1": {
      "name": "Skill 1: Butterfly",
      "description": "[Tag] Enhancement, movement speed reduction, damage\nCD: 8 seconds / MP consumption: 60\nReleases a phantom butterfly in a fan-shaped area and strengthens passive skills for 2 seconds. The butterfly deals 400 (400 + 72% of magic attack) magic damage to enemies within range and reduces enemy movement speed by 30% for 2 seconds.\n[Basic damage] Lv.1: 400 / Lv.2: 480 / Lv.3: 560 / Lv.4: 640 / Lv.5: 720 / Lv.6: 800\n[Movement speed reduction] Lv.1: 30% / Lv.2: 36% / Lv.3: 42% / Lv.4: 48% / Lv.5: 54% / Lv.6: 60%"
    },
    "skill2": {
      "name": "Skill 2: Butterfly Dream",
      "description": "[Tag] Damage, movement speed increase\nCD: 4.5 seconds / MP consumption: 35\nDeals 250 (250 + 40% of magic attack) magic damage to nearby enemies and applies 1 stack of engraving, and each stack deals 125 (125 + 20% of magic attack) magic damage to the target for 5 seconds. Maximum 5 stacks. At the same time, give 1 stack of Imprint to yourself and nearby friendly heroes, and each stack increases the target's movement speed by 3%. Maximum of 5 stacks, duration is 5 seconds. Passive effect: Activates skill 2 once every 7 seconds.\n[Cooldown] Lv.1: 4.5 / Lv.2: 4.3 / Lv.3: 4.1 / Lv.4: 4.0 / Lv.5: 3.8 / Lv.6: 3.6\n[Basic damage] Lv.1: 250 / Lv.2: 300 / Lv.3: 350 / Lv.4: 400 / Lv.5: 450 / Lv.6: 500\n[Increases with each stack] Lv.1: 125 / Lv.2: 150 / Lv.3: 175 / Lv.4: 200 / Lv.5: 225 / Lv.6: 250"
    },
    "skill3": {
      "name": "Skill 3: Tenjin Unity",
      "description": "[Tag] CC release, super armor, shield\nCD: 60 seconds / MP consumption: 150\nBy deploying a dream realm, it removes CC from self and nearby allied heroes, and also grants a 700 (700 + 13% of additional HP) shield and CC immunity to self and allied heroes for 2 seconds.\n[Cooldown] Lv.1: 60 / Lv.2: 55 / Lv.3: 50\n[Granted Shield] Lv.1: 700 / Lv.2: 1050 / Lv.3: 1400"
    }
  },
