      "playstyle": "In the early stages, you will work together with your ally Carry, and use Skill 1's increased movement speed and knock-up, and Skill 2's Stun to actively capture enemies. This hero's greatest strength lies in conquering towers, so when the enemy has recalled you or you have an advantage in numbers, use your passives and skills to forcefully dive into the tower and quickly destroy objects to give your team an advantage."
