      "playstyle": "In the early stages, play safely and concentrate on farming until the magic absorption item is completed. Once you have all the items, you can demonstrate your true value in group battles, so work with your allies and dive deep into the enemy's territory. The basic strategy is to stay in the center of the enemy while activating your ultimate, dealing both damage and recovery, thereby destroying the enemy's rear guard and ensuring your own survival."
