        "High instantaneous firepower from skill combos, making it easy to gain an advantage in early lane battles and small group battles.",
        "In group battles, his ultimate's wide range attacks and petrification have the potential to completely change the battle situation."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Has low mobility and is easily kited by long-range attacks or enemies with high mobility.",
        "Since the activation of petrification is dependent on probability, there is instability in which CC cannot be determined in important situations.",
        "In the latter half of the game, the influence tends to decrease as the enemy's durability and cooperation increase."
      ],
      "playstyle": "Utilize your early strength to gain an advantage in lane battles, and take control of the match by actively acquiring objects and covering your allies. In group battles, you can make full use of your summoner skill \"Flicker\" to jump in from the enemy's blind spot, and deploy your ultimate to petrify the enemy's rear guard while aiming for massive damage. Rather than rushing in blindly, try to coordinate with your allies' CC or find the right time to take advantage of the enemy's openings."
    },
