        "Highly reliant on healing, making him extremely vulnerable to Anti-Heal items.",
        "Low mobility and lack of escape skills mean he can be easily isolated and killed if his team does not follow up his initiation.",
        "Weak against true damage, percentage-based damage, and heroes who can cleanse taunts."
      ],
      "playstyle": "Focus on farming safely in the Clash Lane during the early game to build defensive items. From mid-game onwards, act as the team's main tank and initiator. Prioritize using your ultimate's AoE taunt on high-threat targets like assassins and marksmen. Charging Skill 1 before leaping with your ultimate allows you to instantly deal damage and heal upon landing, further increasing your survivability and impact."
