        "Can stay in lane indefinitely without recalling due to sustained damage and healing from her passive shadow crows.",
        "Her Ultimate grants untargetability and invincibility, allowing easy gank escapes or tower dives."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Lacks large-scale CC or burst damage, reducing her impact in large team fights.",
        "Highly reliant on her skills; missing her Skill 2 tether drastically drops her damage and healing.",
        "Vulnerable to hard CC; getting chain-CCed before casting her Ultimate usually results in a quick death."
      ],
      "playstyle": "Play her primarily in the Clash Lane (or Jungle) and abuse her overwhelming 1v1 potential to completely shut down your opponent. Rather than grouping for 5v5 team fights, capitalize on her self-sufficiency by split-pushing and taking down towers. If multiple enemies come to defend, use your Ultimate's invincibility combined with your Skill 1 mobility to escape safely, effectively splitting the enemy team's formation and resources."
