        "Deals significant damage to enemy towers and objectives, granting strong lane suppression.",
        "His passive healing while standing in fire domains gives him excellent durability and sustain in lane."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Low mobility and lack of movement skills make him very vulnerable to dives from high-mobility assassins.",
        "Since self-healing is one of his strengths, his effectiveness can be heavily limited by enemy anti-heal items."
      ],
      "playstyle": "Zhou Yu is a formation-based mage who sets up fire domains with Skill 2 and spreads them with the wind from Skill 1. A powerful combo involves keeping enemies at a distance with large areas of fire, then hitting them with Skill 3 while they touch the flames to stun them. He should maintain a safe position to spread fire and effectively suppress towers and objectives."
