    "passive": {
      "name": "Passive: Occult Arts - Manipulation",
      "description": "When the Main Body's or Puppet's attacks hit an enemy hero (basic attacks have a 30% chance), Yango gains Hero Shards (non-hero units are excluded) and heals for 70 (70 + 1% extra Max HP). The healing skill changes to 'Shard Bag'. Can store up to 150 Hero Shards to synthesize a hero Puppet. Automatically gains 1 Hero Shard every 10–5 seconds. Hero Puppet: Consumes 50 Hero Shards to transform the Puppet into the corresponding enemy hero (same appearance, lasts 10s). The Puppet deals 50% damage and takes 100% extra damage. (For every 15 extra Physical Attack the Main Body has, Puppet damage increases by 1%; for every 80 extra HP, damage taken decreases by 2%).",
      "tags": [
