    "skill1": {
      "name": "Skill 1: Occult Arts - Umbra",
      "description": "Casts the Puppet, dealing 300 (300 + 100% extra Physical Attack) physical damage and knocking up enemies in its path for 0.5s. Afterwards, controls the Puppet. The Puppet's basic attacks deal 100% of physical attack as physical damage. When the Puppet is recalled, the Main Body gains a Purify effect, 40% increased Movement Speed, and a 420 (420 + 6% extra Max HP) shield for 1s. If the Puppet is destroyed, the Main Body is revealed, stunned for 2s, and cannot summon the Puppet for 20–16s. The Puppet is automatically destroyed if it remains over 2500 units away from the Main Body for 5s. Normal Puppet: Inherits equipment effects (excluding Resurrection, Rage, Dark Curtain, Mana Shield) and some buff effects. Gold and EXP are shared with the Main Body.",
