    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Incredibly versatile with 8 different skills between his Main Body and Puppet, offering immense outplay potential.",
        "Can safely secure vision and split-push by mimicking enemies or remotely controlling his Puppet while hiding his Main Body.",
        "High burst damage potential; can easily assassinate the enemy backline by catching them with the Puppet and swapping positions."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Highly complex skill set with a steep learning curve, requiring extensive practice to master the combos.",
        "The Main Body is extremely squishy and will die almost instantly if caught by crowd control.",
        "If the Puppet is destroyed, the Main Body is stunned for a long duration, leaving him completely exposed."
      ],
      "playstyle": "A highly technical assassin who hides his Main Body in a safe location while sending his Puppet into the enemy formation to scout or ambush. His core combo involves catching an enemy carry with the Puppet, swapping positions with his Main Body, and unleashing massive burst damage. Keep track of enemy skills and positions, and look for the perfect moment to assassinate the backline."
    },
    "meta": {
      "summoner_spells": [
