        "CC",
        "ダメージ"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD : 16秒",
      "description": "Throws his chain blade in the target direction. The chain blade stops when it reaches its maximum range or hits an enemy. The chain blade stuns the first enemy hit for 1s, dealing 420 (420 + 10% extra Max HP) physical damage to nearby enemies, and pulls Dun to the blade's location. Upon arrival, deals an additional 420 (420 + 10% extra Max HP) physical damage to nearby enemies. Dun is immune to CC while casting this skill.",
