        "Extremely strong in 1v1s and chaotic brawls due to his Ultimate's massive lifesteal and self-buffs.",
        "Possesses multiple chainable dashes, allowing for flexible engages, disengages, and chasing.",
        "Combines CC cleanse, CC immunity, and healing to endure enemy attacks and hold the frontline."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Needs to stick to targets to land basic attacks, making him weak to heavy CC or kiting that restricts his movement.",
        "Struggles to exert his strengths against burst-heavy team comps or enemies who build anti-heal items."
      ],
      "playstyle": "A highly mobile, self-healing Fighter designed to dive the enemy backline and deal sustained damage. The core combo involves weaving basic attacks between his Skill 1 slashes to maximize output, then popping his Ultimate when his HP drops to heal massively while continuing to fight. Wait for the enemy's main CC skills to be burned before fully committing to the engage."
    },
