    "passive": {
      "name": "Passive: Niten Ichiryuu",
      "description": "Casting a skill grants 1 stack of Vigor (up to 2 stacks). Based on the current number of stacks, his next basic attack is enhanced differently and consumes 1 Vigor. Enhanced basic attacks are not affected by attack speed, and hitting an enemy reduces the cooldowns of Skill 1 and Skill 2 by 1s.\n1 Stack of Vigor:\nIf the target's HP is above 50%, the next basic attack becomes a dual-sword slash, dealing an additional 120 (120 + 40% extra Physical Attack) physical damage.\nIf the target's HP is below 50%, the next basic attack becomes a vertical slash, dealing 45 (45 + 15% extra Physical Attack) plus 6% of the target's lost Max HP as physical damage.\n2 Stacks of Vigor:\nDashes towards the target, dealing 187 (20 + 100% Physical Attack) physical damage and slowing them by 25% for 1s.",
