        "Overwhelming mobility with multiple dashes and incredible outplay potential due to his untargetability (invincibility) states.",
        "Skill 2 shreds enemy armor, allowing his Ultimate's AoE damage to easily wipe out squishy targets.",
        "If he gains an early lead, his snowball potential is virtually unmatched."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "His Ultimate is locked behind his passive; if he cannot stack basic attacks safely, he cannot fight effectively.",
        "Extremely fragile. If he is hit by hard CC before he can enter his untargetable state, he will die instantly."
      ],
      "playstyle": "An incredibly elusive and high-difficulty assassin who relies on hit-and-run tactics. The core gameplay loop involves stacking his passive on jungle monsters or minions to unlock his Ultimate, then using his Skill 1 dashes to quickly enter the team fight, dropping Skill 2 and his Ultimate, and finally using the 3rd cast of Skill 1 to snap back to safety. Keep track of enemy CC skills and always have a safe spot to retreat to."
    },
    "meta": {
      "summoner_spells": [
        "Smite"
      ],
      "synergy": [
        {
