        "Possesses multiple mobility skills, giving him incredible kiting potential and survivability for a marksman.",
        "Excels at safely poking down enemies from a distance with Skill 1."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "His ultimate is his main source of AoE damage, but it is easily interrupted by any enemy CC.",
        "Lacks any form of crowd control himself, making him unable to peel for himself or setup kills for his team.",
        "Uses energy instead of mana; missing his poke means he will quickly run out of energy and become useless."
      ],
      "playstyle": "Focus entirely on farming in the early game to hit your Attack Speed thresholds (like Doomsday) to increase your bullet count. From the mid-game onward, constantly use Skill 1 to poke from afar, applying your passive and whittling down the enemy's health using hit-and-run tactics. In team fights, NEVER initiate with your ultimate; wait until the enemy has used their CC skills, then dash in with Fevered Barrage to clean up the fight."
