      "strengths": [
        "Unmatched strength in extended team fights due to passive healing and true damage.",
        "The invincibility frame on Skill 2's dash allows her to dodge enemy attacks and CC.",
        "Ultimate drastically reduces skill cooldowns, allowing her to spam high damage output."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Extremely vulnerable to hard CC (especially suppression); she will die instantly if locked down.",
        "Must fight in close-to-mid range despite being a Mage, which is highly risky.",
        "Very mana-hungry, and anti-heal items significantly drop her survivability."
      ],
      "playstyle": "Unlike standard Mages, she fights in close quarters. In team fights, wait for the enemy to use their hard CC (like suppression or stuns) before going in. Deploy your Ultimate and spam Skill 1 and 2 rapidly within its range, constantly applying true damage and healing yourself. Mastering the invincibility frames of Skill 2 to dodge attacks is mandatory, and pairing it with the 'Purify' spell is crucial for staying alive."
