      "playstyle": "Farm efficiently in the early game as a standard jungler, looking for secure ganks to gain resources. In team fights, do not engage first; wait for your tanks to absorb enemy CC before diving the backline. Utilize skill combos to repeatedly reset your Ultimate, performing hit-and-run attacks to weave in and out of the fight."
