    "meta": {
      "summoner_spells": [
        "Flash"
      ],
      "synergy": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Zhuangzi",
          "reason": "This is because it provides damage reduction and CC nullification, increasing safety when Hana Mulan dives deep into enemy territory.",
          "hero_id": "hero_015"
        }
      ],
      "counters": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Liang",
          "reason": "This is because a powerful hard CC targeting the target will completely restrain him before he can unleash the high firepower of his heavy sword form.",
          "hero_id": "hero_049"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Mi Yue",
          "reason": "Because of his high mobility and sustain ability, he can avoid and absorb Hana Mulan's combos, and on the other hand, his stamina is reduced.",
          "hero_id": "hero_023"
        }
      ]
    },
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "You can switch between dual sword mode (mobility and silence) and heavy sword mode (damage reduction and high firepower) to fight flexibly according to the situation.",
        "It has a high ability to silence targets with combos in twin sword mode and take down isolated targets without allowing counterattacks.",
        "While in heavy sword mode, he gains super armor and up to 50% damage reduction, allowing him to unleash his firepower even in team fights."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "A hero for advanced players whose mode switching and combo operations are extremely complex and require a lot of practice to become proficient.",
        "If you receive a strong CC chain before approaching, you will be defeated before you can withstand it in heavy sword mode.",
        "If you play against a fighter with strong early lane play or a tank with high sustain (recovery), it's easy to fall behind in farming."
      ],
      "playstyle": "In the early stages, avoid unnecessary trades and focus on farming safely to get core items and Cooldown Reduction. From the mid-game onwards, use your mobility to push the side lanes and launch a surprise attack on the enemy's carries. The basic strategy is to instantly close the distance with a combo that combines flash and skills, and immediately after inflicting silence with the twin swords, switch to the heavy sword and inflict burst damage all at once."
    }
  },
