      "playstyle": "Operate as a mid laner or roamer, focusing on safely farming and clearing waves in the early stages. Once you have mastered the ultimate, you should actively roam to the side lanes and work with your allies to aim for a kill. In team fights, always take a position behind your allies and be sure to use your ultimate against enemy assassins and carries to neutralize them."
