    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Overwhelming burst damage that can instantly kill soft heroes in the back line.",
        "Extremely high mobility due to abundant blink skills and movement ability.",
        "Powerful poke performance from a safe distance using Skill 2 (Hanacho Fan)."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Since energy (kiri) is used instead of mana, skills will become unusable if not properly managed.",
        "Combo accuracy and engagement timing are critical, making it extremely difficult to operate.",
        "It is difficult to demonstrate its strengths against hard CC (action obstruction) and highly durable shield holders."
      ],
      "playstyle": "In the early stages, use skill 2 to poke from a distance in the mid lane and safely reduce your health while farming. After pushing the wave, intervene in the side lanes and pick off isolated enemies. In group battles, the Assassin's move is to not rush in first, but to wait for the enemy's CC and defense skills to be used up, then hit the carry group in the rear with a combo all at once and then leave."
    },
    "meta": {
      "summoner_spells": [
        "epiphany"
      ],
      "synergy": [
