    "skill3": {
      "name": "Skill 3: Sky Melody",
      "tags": [
        "reset"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD: 0s",
      "description": "After a short chant, resets the skill with the longest cooldown for one ally within range, and your own skill CD becomes 10 (+120% of your ally's CD).\nIf an ally does not activate the reset skill, the cooldown of \"Sky Melody\" will be reduced by 20%. Allies can activate the reset skill within 5 seconds without any MP cost, and share the defeat reward obtained from that skill with the mermaid diva.\nThe order of priority for resetting skills is the contracted party, the non-contracted ally, and the mermaid diva. If the skill cannot be reset, the cooldown of \"Sky Melody\" will be greatly reduced.",
      "table": {
        "headers": [
