    "status_text": "status\nBasic status\nMax HP 3359\nMax MP 560\nPhysical Attack 186(176+10)\nMagic attack 0\nPhysical Defense 150|20%\nMagic defense 75|11.1%\nattack status\nMovement Speed 385\nPhysical Pierce 0|0%\nMagic defense penetration 0|0%\nAttack Speed 5%\nCritical Rate 0%\nCritical Damage 200%\nPhysical life steal 0%\nMagic life steal 0%\nCooldown Reduction 0%\nAttack Range close range\ndefense status\nResistance 0%\nHP Regen/5s 47\nMana Regen/5s 14",
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Extremely high instantaneous firepower that can instantly defeat isolated soft targets.",
        "With its excellent mobility, it can quickly move around the map and easily apply pressure.",
        "Clearing the jungle after the middle stage when all the core items are available is fast, and it's easy to control the tempo."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "It is extremely vulnerable to enemy CC (control), and if it is stopped during a combo, it is likely to be defeated without being able to do anything.",
        "It is difficult to jump into enemy formations where there are supports with high peel ability (skills to protect allies).",
        "It is not suitable for a simple frontal breakthrough, and if the enemy's defense network is in place, the field of action will be limited."
      ],
      "playstyle": "As a jungler, you can quickly farm to level 4 in the early stages and use your mobility to proactively gank and control the tempo of the match. From the middle onwards, build up the Cooldown Reduction and run around the entire map to pick up isolated enemies. In group battles, the basic rule is never to charge head-on, but wait for the enemy's CC skills to be used, then jump into the enemy's carry from the side or rear, quickly kill it, and then leave."
    },
    "meta": {
      "summoner_spells": [
        "punishment"
      ],
      "synergy": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Jin Hime",
          "reason": "Because it provides a wide range of CC and allows Nakoruru to safely deal burst damage.",
          "hero_id": "hero_028"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Oniyako",
          "reason": "Because it gathers enemies while giving stealth and defense down, and can perfectly support Nakoruru's assault.",
          "hero_id": "hero_072"
        }
      ],
      "counters": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Zhang Fei",
          "reason": "Because it can neutralize Nakoruru's bursts and dives with its powerful shield and knockback.",
          "hero_id": "hero_058"
