    "status_text": "status\nBasic status\nMax HP 3748(3628+120)\nMax MP 0\nPhysical Attack 175\nMagic attack 0\nPhysical Defense 150|20%\nMagic defense 75|11.1%\nattack status\nMovement Speed 385\nPhysical Pierce 0|0%\nMagic defense penetration 0|0%\nAttack Speed 0%\nCritical Rate 0%\nCritical Damage 200%\nPhysical life steal 0%\nMagic life steal 0%\nCooldown Reduction 0%\nAttack Range close range\ndefense status\nResistance 0%\nHP Regen/5s 55\nMana Regen/5s 0",
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Skill 1's \"silence\" effect can suppress highly skill-dependent enemies and highly mobile heroes.",
        "High automatic HP recovery through passive skills and excellent durability due to compatibility with defensive items.",
        "The operation is simple and intuitive, and even beginners can perform their tasks reliably."
