      "weaknesses": [
        "It is difficult to utilize the strength of durability against enemies with percentage damage or high armor penetration.",
        "It lacks the firepower to cut through enemies on its own, and tends to rely on damage follow-up from allies.",
        "It cannot pose a threat unless you get close to it, so it is vulnerable to kiting."
      ],
      "playstyle": "When fighting in the crash lane or as the team's main tank, he uses his natural resilience to stay in the lane and stand on the front lines as a shield for his allies. In group battles, use Skill 1's increased Movement Speed to charge at the enemy's carry group, and apply \"silence\" to thoroughly disrupt the opponent's key players. By managing the cooldown and mastering ``Double Silence'', which allows you to hit Skill 1 continuously, you can create a decisive chance for your allies to kill without allowing the enemy to counterattack."
    },
    "meta": {
      "summoner_spells": [
        "execution",
        "epiphany"
      ],
      "synergy": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Luban No. 7",
          "reason": "This allows you to unleash high firepower from a safe position in time for Arthur's silence or launch.",
          "hero_id": "hero_009"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Aji",
          "reason": "This allows Arthur to silence his enemies while ensuring that he can assassinate them from behind.",
          "hero_id": "hero_018"
        }
      ],
      "counters": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Lu Bu",
          "reason": "Because it ignores Arthur's defense power with guaranteed damage and can easily chip away at the entire shield.",
          "hero_id": "hero_024"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "hot month",
          "reason": "With his high self-healing power and mobility, he can neutralize and overwhelm Arthur's close combat and continuous combat.",
          "hero_id": "hero_023"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
