    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Overwhelming critical burst damage from an enhanced normal attack after using a skill.",
        "High mobility with abundant blinks allows for flexible pursuit and escape.",
        "Skill 1 nullifies the enemy's skills and has an invincible shield, making it easy to survive even if you jump into enemy territory."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "There is a high degree of dependence on core items (critical items), and if you are late with gold, it will easily become air.",
        "It is weak to hard CC, and if stopped in the middle of a combo, it will be defeated easily due to its low durability.",
        "A high degree of skill is required to bring out the maximum potential, such as skill 1's defense timing."
      ],
      "playstyle": "As a jungler, in the early stages, focus on farming without wasting anything and quickly getting level 4 and essential equipment. Once your equipment is ready, use your mobility to attack mages and marksmen with low health, and fulfill your role as an assassin by instantly dissolving them. In group fights, instead of taking the lead, wait for the enemy's main CC to be used up and then aim for carries from the sides or behind, using Skill 1's invincibility to prevent counterattacks and secure a kill."
    },
