      "playstyle": "Farm efficiently, mainly in the jungle, and take advantage of your early strength to actively aim for ganks and acquiring objects. In group battles, the basic idea is to act like an assassin, rather than charging head-on like a tank. Exploit the gap right after the enemy's main interfering skill is used, deploy your ultimate shield, and jump into the rear carry to defeat them all at once."
