        "Crowd Control"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD: 40s",
      "description": "Roars in the specified direction and creates a storm, gaining a shield equal to 40% of maximum HP for 15 seconds. While roaring, nullifies CC for 1.25 seconds and becomes invincible. The storm blows enemies away, dealing 600 (600 + 150% of additional physical attack) physical damage and stunning enemies at the edge of the storm for 1.5 seconds. Movement speed increases by 50% while in a storm.\nDemon mode: When in demon mode, deals an additional 220 (220 + 100% of additional physical attack) damage when attacking normally. When demon mode ends, the skill effect of \"Forbidden Area\" is automatically activated.",
      "icon": "/images/skills/hero_058_skill3.png",
      "forms": [
        {
          "form_name": "Human Form",
          "description": "Roars in the specified direction and creates a storm, gaining a shield equal to 40% of maximum HP for 15 seconds. While roaring, nullifies CC for 1.25 seconds and becomes invincible. The storm blows enemies away, dealing 600 (600 + 150% of additional physical attack) physical damage and stunning enemies at the edge of the storm for 1.5 seconds. Movement speed increases by 50% while in a storm.\nDemon mode: When in demon mode, deals an additional 220 (220 + 100% of additional physical attack) damage when attacking normally. When demon mode ends, the skill effect of \"Forbidden Area\" is automatically activated.",
