      "description": "Fight by switching between the five soldiers (armor, spear, sword, sword, and bow). Each hit with a normal attack restores 20 HP (20 + 0.3% of additional HP) and switches to the next weapon with longer range. Gain 1 stack of Fighting Spirit for each normal attack/skill hit (duration: 4 seconds, maximum of 8 stacks). Each stack of fighting spirit increases attack speed by 4% (possible to break attack speed limit).\nWhen the weapon is a spear and spear, it is in protection mode, when it is a halberd and a sword, it is in attack mode, and when it is a bow, it is in super killing mode.\nThe effects of Skills 1 and 2 change in each mode, and when you switch to Super Kill mode, the CD of Skills 1 and 2 will be reduced by 50%.",
