      "strengths": [
        "Versatility that can be used in any situation with a unique system that switches between 5 weapons.",
        "High burst firepower and mobility at maximum passive stack (overkill state)"
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Operation and situational judgment are highly difficult, such as managing weapons and maintaining stacks.",
        "It is difficult to cut down tank heroes with high HP and high defense power."
      ],
      "playstyle": "You are mainly in charge of crash lanes and jungles, and fight while switching weapons depending on the situation. Before a battle, it is essential to accumulate passive stacks with normal attacks and be ready to go into \"overkill state\" and unleash maximum firepower. In group battles, be sure to use the buffs provided by your ultimate to utilize your inherent mobility and instantaneous firepower to quickly eliminate the enemy's rear guard, acting like an assassin."
