        "Haste"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD : 7.5s",
      "description": "Jump up into the air. While active, your movement speed increases and you can jump over terrain.\nA normal attack in the air releases a powerful long-range arrow that deals 475 (230 + 140% of physical attack) physical damage, knocks the enemy back (no CC), and increases the time spent in the air.\nArrow damage increases by 2 for every 1% increase in attack speed.\nIf you do not shoot an arrow in the air, stack enhanced basic attacks with normal range for 3 seconds after landing.\nWhen shooting an arrow in the air, if you move the direction controller in the opposite direction to the target, the arrow will move a certain distance in the input direction after shooting.",
      "table": {
