      "cooldown": "CD : 2s",
      "description": "Throws a wolf soul trap at the specified location. When an enemy comes into contact with it, it gains vision and deals 380 (380 + 90% of additional physical attack) physical damage, summons a wolf soul to that location, and automatically attacks the enemy it comes into contact with.\nUntriggered traps become stealthed 2 seconds after being set. Up to 4 traps can be set at the same time.\nThe Wolf Spirit inherits 25% of the Blue Wolf Descendant's basic stats, and has a 50% critical hit effect. Wolf Spirit reduces the target's movement speed by 5%-10% for 1 second with each attack (maximum of 5 stacks).",
