      "cooldown": "CD : 50s",
      "description": "Summons wolf souls (2 + number of stacks of skill 2) in the specified direction and charges them, consuming stacks of skill 2 to activate surrounding traps.\nGains cavalry ability (can perform normal attacks while moving), increases movement speed by 10%, physical attack by 50, and attack speed by 20% for 8 seconds.\nDuring normal attacks, wolf souls without targets attack together.",
