    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Overwhelming burst damage when hitting at the intersection of skills that draw unique trajectories",
        "Ultra-long range that allows for unilateral poke and minion processing from a distance."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "The difficulty of hitting the unique curved skill trajectory is extremely high, and the degree of dependence on player skill is extremely high.",
        "They have poor self-defense skills and are extremely vulnerable when approached by assassins etc."
      ],
      "playstyle": "A turret type mage that delivers overwhelming firepower from behind. Increase your accuracy by always maintaining a safe position and firing skills when the vanguard is engaged or when your allies are CCing you. Strengthen your skills with the ultimate and aim to kill the enemy carry by hitting multiple swords at the same time. High aiming ability and spatial awareness are required."
    },
