      "description": "Hold up a shield and gain a 1200 (1200 + 16% additional physical) shield (CC disabled while active). After 1.5 seconds, counterattack with the holy shield and deal 450 (450 + 150% of additional physical) magic damage to enemies within range. Every time you take damage from an enemy hero while the shield is up, the counterattack damage from the holy shield is increased by 10% and the activation time is reduced by 10% (up to 5 stacks).",
      "icon": "/images/skills/hero_069_skill3.png",
