          "form_name": "Battle Cry",
          "description": "Move to the nearest friendly tower. When taking off, it deals 600 (600 + 180% of physical attack) physical damage (increases according to hero level) to enemies within range and knocks them up for 0.75 seconds. At the same time, protect surrounding allies and move them together to the tower.\nIf the resurrection time is less than 10 seconds, active skills cannot be used.\nIf Skill 3 is activated during death, protection of allies and subsequent effects cannot be applied upon resurrection.",
