          "reason": "Engagement can be easily hindered by mobility buffs and silence skills.",
          "hero_id": "hero_020"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Guan Yu",
          "reason": "With his high mobility and forced movement skills, he can completely miss the target of skill combos.",
          "hero_id": "hero_039"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
