    "status_text": "Max HP: 3429\nMax Mana: 620\nPhysical Attack: 168\nMagical Attack: 0\nPhysical Defense: 150|20%\nMagical Defense: 75|11.1%\nMovement Speed: 365\nPhysical Pierce: 0|0%\nMagical Pierce: 0|0%\nAttack Speed: 5%\nCrit Rate: 0%\nCrit Damage: 200%\nPhysical Lifesteal: 0%\nMagical Lifesteal: 0%\nCooldown Reduction: 0%\nAttack Range: Ranged\nResistance: 0%\nHP Regen/5s: 80\nMana Regen/5s: 15",
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Un-cleansable suppression and damage sharing from his Ultimate guarantees the neutralization of enemy carries and assassins.",
        "Overwhelming melee prowess in the early game thanks to the continuous healing provided by his dark orbs."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Lacks mobility skills, making him easily kited by ranged enemies.",
        "His durability relies heavily on healing, so anti-heal items greatly reduce his effectiveness."
      ],
      "playstyle": "An aggressive support that invades the enemy jungle early to apply pressure. In teamfights, maintain 3 orbs while threatening the frontline, and look for opportunities to cast your Ultimate on the enemy's main damage dealers or assassins diving your backline. Target selection for your Ultimate is crucial (never use it on an enemy tank), ensuring your team can follow up and secure the kill."
    },
