    "status_text": "Max HP: 3394\nMax Mana: 620\nPhysical Attack: 166\nMagical Attack: 10 (0+10)\nPhysical Defense: 150|20%\nMagical Defense: 75|11.1%\nMovement Speed: 365\nPhysical Pierce: 0|0%\nMagical Pierce: 0|0%\nAttack Speed: 5%\nCrit Rate: 0%\nCrit Damage: 200%\nPhysical Lifesteal: 0%\nMagical Lifesteal: 0%\nCooldown Reduction: 0%\nAttack Range: Ranged\nResistance: 0%\nHP Regen/5s: 47\nMana Regen/5s: 15",
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "One of the best initiation tools in the game with his Skill 2's AoE pull and stun.",
        "Ultimate provides team-wide stealth, acceleration, and powerful defense-shredding debuffs."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "His pull is useless without follow-up damage from teammates, making communication essential (hard in solo queue).",
        "Must dive into the middle of the enemy team, but lacks the durability of a true tank, making him fragile when focused."
      ],
      "playstyle": "An aggressive support that coordinates with teammates to wipe out enemies instantly. Instead of engaging frontally, use stealth to approach from blind spots and target the backline carries. The core combo is 'Ultimate -> Skill 1 -> Skill 2' to gather enemies into one spot for your team's AoE damage. Items focusing on cooldown reduction and movement speed are highly recommended."
    },
    "meta": {
