      "description": "Summons a magic circle that lasts for 4s and provides vision. When it expires, it teleports one ally back to the spawn point, cleansing all debuffs and allowing them to return to their original position via the crystal's warp point. If no ally hero is warped, it leaves a mark that recalls the first ally to touch it. Activating again removes the mark. Cooldown is reduced by 50% if no ally hero is warped. Da Qiao gets priority for the warp and instantly recalls if she touches the mark.",
