      "name": "Whirlpool of the Sea",
      "description": "Summons a massive magic circle at a designated location, dealing 500 (+90% Magical Attack) magical damage to enemies within. The circle lasts 8s. Allies can tap the Whirlpool portal to teleport to the circle. Da Qiao and allies within the circle gain a 350 (+50% Magical Attack) shield, while Da Qiao gains an extra shield equal to 7% of her bonus Max HP.",
