      "weaknesses": [
        "Rooting himself in his Ultimate makes him a stationary, easy target.",
        "Low mobility and self-peel make him extremely vulnerable to assassins and long-range engage."
      ],
      "playstyle": "Play safely in the early game to farm gold and complete your core items. In teamfights, never engage first. Position yourself behind your frontline or tanks before deploying your Ultimate. Wait for enemies to burn their gap-closers before entering Artillery Mode, or rely on your standard basic attacks to kite them out."
