    "status_text": "Max HP: 3105\nMax Mana: 0\nPhysical Attack: 159 (159+0)\nMagical Attack: 0\nPhysical Defense: 150|20%\nMagical Defense: 75|11.1%\nMovement Speed: 380\nPhysical Pierce: 0|0%\nMagical Pierce: 0|0%\nAttack Speed: 0%\nCrit Rate: 0%\nCrit Damage: 200%\nPhysical Lifesteal: 0%\nMagical Lifesteal: 0%\nCooldown Reduction: 0%\nAttack Range: Melee\nResistance: 0%\nHP Regen/5s: 48\nMana Regen/5s: 0",
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Unmatched shield generation and passive stat scaling make him incredibly tanky in protracted fights.",
        "His mixed damage profile (Physical/Magical) makes him very hard for the enemy to build defenses against."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Easily kited due to limited range and reliance on keeping up Mass for combat stats.",
        "Very susceptible to true damage and shield-breaking effects like true damage marksmen."
      ],
      "playstyle": "In the laning phase, leverage your thick shields to out-trade enemies and aggressively push the lane. Manage your Mass carefully by continuously casting skills before fights. In teamfights, use your Ultimate to dive into the enemy backline, soak up damage with your shields, and disrupt their formation."
    },
