      "description": "Fires an energy bullet, dealing 250 (250 + 30% of magic damage) magic damage to enemies along the route. If it detects an enemy hero before reaching the end point, it will track the enemy, dealing magic damage, knocking it up for 0.5 seconds, and gaining vision for 5 seconds.\nPossessed state: Tracking range increases by 20%.\nDeer state: quickly returns to human form.",
