      "icon": "/images/skills/hero_086_skill3.png"
    },
    "status_text": "Basic status\nMax HP 3218\nMax aura 450\nPhysical attack 181 (171+10)\nMagic attack 0\nPhysical defense 150|20%\nMagic defense 75|11.1%\nattack status\nMovement speed 380\nPhysical defense penetration 0|0%\nMagic defense penetration 0|0%\nAttack speed bonus 5%\nCritical rate 0%\nCritical effect 200%\nPhysical life steal 0%\nMagic life steal 0%\nCooldown reduction 0%\nAttack range close range\ndefense status\nResistance 0%\nHP recovery every 5 seconds 49\nAura recovery every 5 seconds 0",
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "It has overwhelming mobility that allows it to fly ignoring the terrain, and is good at surprise attacks and jungle invasions from unpredictable routes.",
        "Utilizing his mobility, he has extremely high map pressure in the early stages, and can always force enemy laners to be on guard.",
        "Excellent ability to quickly dive into the enemy's rear guard (Marksman or Mage) and instantly deal burst damage and kill them."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Its combat power is completely dependent on its flight status, and it will be greatly weakened if it takes too much damage or lands out of energy.",
        "The Assassin's fate is that it has low durability, and if it gets caught by CC when diving into the enemy's territory, it is likely to be defeated without being able to escape.",
        "In group battles in the final stages, enemies form dense formations, making it difficult to kill them alone and reducing their influence."
      ],
      "playstyle": "Make the most of your flying ability, which allows you to ignore the terrain, and proactively gank and steal neutral monsters from the enemy's blind spots from the beginning. During battle, energy management is essential to maintain flight status, and if the gauge is about to run out, you need to be calm enough to leave and recover. In group battles, don't rush in headfirst, but wait until the enemy's CC skills are used up, and make sure to assassinate the enemy's defenseless rear carry."
    },
    "meta": {
      "summoner_spells": [
        "punishment"
      ],
      "synergy": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Oniyako",
          "reason": "Because he can restrain the enemy with strong CC and ensure Yunzhongjun's dive into the back line.",
          "hero_id": "hero_072"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Yaria",
          "reason": "To increase Yunzhongjun's survivability and kill line with shields and additional CC to help him safely escape.",
          "hero_id": "hero_085"
        }
      ],
      "counters": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Zhang Liang",
          "reason": "This is because you can forcibly shoot down Yunzhongjun, who flies in while in flight, using target suppression CC.",
          "hero_id": "hero_049"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "East Emperor Taichi",
          "reason": "This is because you can restrain Yunzhongjun who dives without missing with a guaranteed suppression CC and lead to a kill.",
          "hero_id": "hero_071"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "hero_087": {
    "hero_id": "087",
    "hero_name": "Li Xin",
    "hero_title": "Sword of the World",
    "role": "Fighter",
    "sub_role": "Berserker type Fighter",
    "difficulty": "Normal",
    "stats": {
      "survival": 4,
      "attack": 8,
      "skill": 5,
      "difficulty": 6
    },
    "status_text": "Basic status\nMax HP 3512\nMax MP 0\nPhysical attack 190 (180+10)\nMagic attack 0\nPhysical defense 150|20%\nMagic defense 75|11.1%\nattack status\nMovement speed 375\nPhysical defense penetration 0|0%\nMagic defense penetration 0|0%\nAttack speed bonus 5%\nCritical rate 0%\nCritical effect 200%\nPhysical life steal 0%\nMagic life steal 0%\nCooldown reduction 0%\nAttack range close range\ndefense status\nResistance 0%\nHP recovery every 5 seconds 52\nMP recovery every 5 seconds 0",
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "You can use either light form (for long-distance poke and group battles) and dark form (for close combat and split push) depending on the situation.",
        "1v1 performance in dark form and tower destruction speed are extremely high, allowing pressure to be applied to the entire map.",
        "In light form, it has high burst damage and wide-range attacks, and can quickly whittle down the enemy's health from medium range."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "It is difficult to operate as it is necessary to accurately understand the strengths and weaknesses of each form and use maneuvers and combos according to the situation.",
        "Both forms are weak against heavy Hard CC, making it difficult to deal with compositions that have a wealth of enemy interference skills.",
        "The dark form is not suitable for 5v5 group battles, and if you do not keep pace with your allies, there is a risk of being isolated and defeated individually."
      ],
      "playstyle": "The basic idea is to decide in advance your main form (light or dark) according to the match situation and your own play style, and create a build that specializes in that form. If you choose dark form, avoid group fights and use split pushes to keep pushing the side lanes and dividing the enemy's attention. If you choose the light form, you will be required to shoot powerful ranged skills from behind the front line of your allies and deal maximum damage as the key to team battles."
    },
    "meta": {
      "summoner_spells": [
        "epiphany",
        "teleportation"
      ],
      "synergy": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Oniyako",
          "reason": "Stealth and pull make it easier to reliably hit multiple enemies with Light Li Xin's powerful ranged ult.",
          "hero_id": "hero_072"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Tsai Wenji",
          "reason": "With recovery and CC, it safely supports Dark Li Xin's approach and Light Li Xin's poke.",
          "hero_id": "hero_070"
        }
      ],
      "counters": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Zhang Fei",
          "reason": "Because you can easily block Li Xin's burst damage and approach with a strong shield and knockback.",
          "hero_id": "hero_058"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Alein",
          "reason": "This is because his timer ability in the final stages is extremely high, and he can stop Yami Li Xin's strength, the split push.",
          "hero_id": "hero_091"
        }
      ]
    },
    "passive": {
      "forms": [
        {
          "form_name": "Initial form",
          "name": "Passive: Ashen Razor",
          "description": "Initial mode: Gain 10 EXP when a normal attack or Assault Slash hits a hero.\nDominance Mode: Increases physical damage reduction by 0.15% for every 1% additional attack speed. This effect increases by 50% when you gain control energy. (Increases up to 100% depending on the amount of dominant energy)\nBerserk Mode: Attack speed increases by 0.1% for every 1.5 additional physical attack power. This effect increases by 50% when you acquire Berserk Energy. (Increases up to 100% depending on Berserk energy amount)\nWhen you switch from initial mode to Domination Mode/Berserk Mode, you will acquire the maximum amount of Domination Energy/Berserk Energy (maximum 100) and consume 10 energy of the mode you are using every second. When switching modes, the energy of the mode before switching becomes 0, and the energy of the mode after switching is acquired (100 - the amount of energy of the mode before switching).",
          "table": null
        },
        {
          "form_name": "Dominant form (light)",
          "name": "Passive: Scorched Strikes",
          "tags": [
            "reinforcement",
            "Cooldown",
            "damage"
          ],
          "description": "Activating the skill will strengthen your next normal attack. Enhanced normal attacks have increased range, become piercing attacks, and deal an additional 50% damage.\nWhen enhanced normal attacks and skills hit, the CD of all skills is reduced by 1 second.\nDominance Mode: Increases physical damage reduction by 0.15% for every 1% additional attack speed. This effect increases by 50% when you gain control energy. (Increases up to 100% depending on the amount of dominant energy)\nBerserk Mode: Attack speed increases by 0.1% for every 1.5 additional physical attack power. This effect increases by 50% when you acquire Berserk Energy. (Increases up to 100% depending on Berserk energy amount)",
          "table": null
        },
        {
          "form_name": "Revenge form (dark)",
          "name": "Passive: Void Slice",
          "description": "[Movement speed increase] [Damage]\nGain 20 movement speed, and each time you use a basic attack, the shadow makes an additional basic attack, dealing 75 (75 + 24% of additional physical attack) physical damage.\nDominance Mode: Increases physical damage reduction by 0.15% for every 1% additional attack speed. This effect increases by 50% when you gain control energy. (Increases up to 100% depending on the amount of dominant energy)\nBerserk Mode: Attack speed increases by 0.1% for every 1.5 additional physical attack power. This effect increases by 50% when you acquire Berserk Energy. (Increases up to 100% depending on Berserk energy amount)",
