      "cooldown": "CD : 20s",
      "description": "Deploys a magic circle around your feet that lasts for 8 seconds. Allied heroes within the magic circle have 20% increased critical hit rate and 30% increased movement speed. When the magic circle expands and disappears, it deals 250 (250 + 40% of physical damage) magic damage to enemies within the range. When you self-disappear the magic circle, your movement speed increases by 20% and your critical rate increases by 20% for 3 seconds.\nPassive: Garo's critical damage applies a 30% Movement Speed ​​Reduction effect to the target for 0.5 seconds. If activated again within 1 second, the effect increases to 50%.",
