    "status_text": "Basic status\nMax HP 3282\nMax MP 600\nPhysical attack 185 (175+10)\nMagic attack 0\nPhysical defense 150|20%\nMagic defense 75|11.1%\nattack status\nMovement speed 365\nPhysical defense penetration 0|0%\nMagic defense penetration 0|0%\nAttack speed bonus 10%\nCritical rate 0%\nCritical effect 200%\nPhysical life steal 0%\nMagic life steal 0%\nCooldown reduction 0%\nAttack range long distance\ndefense status\nResistance 0%\nHP recovery every 5 seconds 39\nMP recovery every 5 seconds 15",
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "It has an overwhelming normal attack range that is the longest in the game, allowing you to attack enemies unilaterally from a safe position.",
        "Because the skill has special shield effect (50% damage increase), it is very strong against tanks and supports that use shields frequently.",
        "The firepower in the final stage when all the items are available is tremendous, and if you can handle it properly, you will have overwhelming carry power that will lead your team to victory."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "It is a glass cannon with no movement skills or self-defense skills, making it extremely vulnerable when approached by enemy Assassins.",
        "Firepower is low in the early stages, and it takes a lot of time and gold to complete core items.",
        "Skills and enhanced normal attacks consume a lot of mana, so if you neglect mana management, you will run out of breath at critical moments."
      ],
      "playstyle": "At the very beginning, don't push yourself too hard and concentrate on earning gold by hunting minions in safe locations such as under the tower. In group battles from the mid-game onward, it's all about positioning yourself to take advantage of your own overwhelming range and continue attacking from the back row of your allies, where enemy attacks will never reach you. Since you don't have self-defense skills, always be on the lookout for the enemy Assassin's location on the minimap, and don't leave a position that can be protected by friendly tanks and Support."
    },
    "meta": {
      "summoner_spells": [
        "epiphany",
        "galloping"
      ],
      "synergy": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Ming",
          "reason": "With firepower and recovery buffs, Garo's overwhelming range and firepower can be further enhanced and snowballed.",
          "hero_id": "hero_082"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Zhang Fei",
          "reason": "With his powerful shield and peel ability, he can protect Garo, who doesn't have escape skills, from the enemy Assassin.",
          "hero_id": "hero_058"
        }
      ],
      "counters": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Marco Polo",
          "reason": "This is because it uses its high mobility to sneak through Garo's range, quickly closing the distance and dealing burst damage.",
          "hero_id": "hero_033"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "King Lanling",
          "reason": "This is because the strong burst damage from stealth can instantly kill Garo even if there is an escort.",
          "hero_id": "hero_046"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
