      "cooldown": "CD: 40 seconds",
      "description": "Board a ship and set sail in the specified direction for 12 seconds. While sailing, you gain super armor effect and gradually increase your movement speed. The ship deals 549 (350 + 120% of physical attack) physical damage to enemy minions or non-large monsters and knocks them back.\nIf you activate the skill again in the specified direction while sailing, you will be able to get off the ship at the specified location. If the ship hits a wall, tower/crystal, large monster, or enemy hero, an explosion will occur before the sailing time ends. The explosion deals 549 (350 + 120% of physical attack) physical damage to enemies within the area and knocks them up for 1-1.5 seconds (proportional to the time traveled). Gain 5 stacks of Fortitude when your ship's explosion hits an enemy.\nWhen the ruler of the ocean is piloting a ship, allied heroes near the ship can board the ship as passengers and sail by tapping a button. If a passenger activates a movement skill, receives a Hard CC, or if the Lord of the Seas disembarks, the passengers also disembark.\nDeals physical damage and knocks back.\nIf you activate the skill again in the specified direction while sailing, you will be able to get off the ship at the specified location. If the ship hits a wall, tower/crystal, large monster, or enemy hero, an explosion will occur before the sailing time ends. The explosion deals 549 (350 + 120% of physical attack) physical damage to enemies within the area and knocks them up for 1-1.5 seconds (proportional to the time traveled). Gain 5 stacks of Fortitude when your ship's explosion hits an enemy.\nWhen the ruler of the ocean is piloting a ship, allied heroes near the ship can board the ship as passengers and sail by tapping a button. If a passenger activates a movement skill, receives a Hard CC, or if the Lord of the Seas disembarks, the passengers also disembark.",
