      "description": "Select a target hero and fly into the air for 1.5 seconds, making them mobile and untargetable. It then hits the ground, dealing 254 (175+45% physical attack) physical damage and 254 (175+45% physical attack) magic damage to enemy heroes. The closer you are to the Blade of Memories, the more damage you receive. Up to 100%. Each time the Blade of Remembrance hits an enemy hero, it gains Imprint and Fury. If the target is an ally, give yourself and that ally a 627 (450+100% physical attack) shield when falling. This shield amount increases by 1/3 for each enemy hero you damage.",
