      "weaknesses": [
        "If your actions are blocked by the CC chain, you risk being defeated without being able to do anything.",
        "Easy to be kited by highly mobile Marksman and Assassin",
        "Although strong in the early stages, it is highly dependent on equipment to demonstrate its true value."
      ],
      "playstyle": "Utilize your strong 1v1 performance from level 1 to gain an advantage in early lane battles and aim for snowballs. From the middle stage onward, manage your anger gauge and fight tenaciously while maximizing your passive recovery and guaranteed damage. Ultimate is effective not only as a means of attack, but also as a means of defense to evade the enemy's deadly skills."
    }
