    "skill1": {
      "name": "Skill 1: Path of Passing",
      "tags": [
        "Movement speed increase",
        "damage",
        "Movement Speed Reduction"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD : 12.5s",
      "description": "Opens the path to death and deals 280 (280 + 95% of additional physical attack) magic damage to the target hit.\nPath of Death accelerates its generation when it touches a wall or the wall of life and death, and deals an additional 150 (150 + 60% of additional physical attack) magic damage on subsequent hits. While on the road, you gain the ability to ignore terrain and increase your movement speed by 50%. When the path first touches a wall, it creates a bridge of death, greatly increasing movement speed when the Halt of Purges crosses it. At the same time, reduce the movement speed of nearby enemies by 15%.\nActivating the skill again will call back the sword and enter shaman mode for 4 seconds. Kills a target with less than 10% HP during a normal attack (750-1500% for monsters, changes depending on hero level).\nThis skill deals the same contact damage to non-hero units, and is automatically recalled when the skill count ends.",
