      "cooldown": "CD : 10s",
      "description": "Swings around with a sword, dealing 200 (200 + 60% of additional physical attack) physical damage to the enemy in front, reducing movement speed by 25% for 1 second, and creating a wall of life and death. Gives a mark to enemies who touch the wall of life and death, and deals 140 (140 + 45% of additional physical attack) magic damage to enemies who touch dead branches and reduces movement speed by 25% for 1 second.\nThe next normal attack will be strengthened, dealing 50% additional damage to the target and recovering 65 (65 + 1.5% of additional maximum HP) HP. If there are targets with the engraving within the attack range, Soul Chain activates the same additional damage and healing effect on all targets with the engraving.\nThis skill knocks back non-hero units. Soul Chain can link up to 3 targets. If linked with a non-hero unit, the healing effect will be 50%.",
