    "status_text": "Basic status\n最大HP 3256\nMax MP 600\nPhysical attack 175 (165+10)\nMagic attack 0\nPhysical defense 150|20%\nMagic defense 75|11.1%\nattack status\nMovement speed 365\nPhysical defense penetration 0|0%\nMagic defense penetration 0|0%\nAttack speed bonus 10%\nCritical rate 0%\nCritical effect 200%\nPhysical life steal 0%\nMagic life steal 0%\nCooldown reduction 0%\nAttack range long distance\ndefense status\nResistance 0%\nHP recovery every 5 seconds 44\nMP recovery every 5 seconds 15",
    "passive": {
      "name": "Passive: Hidden Dragon",
      "description": "Attributes corresponding to the last two skills used by Blue Sky Dragon are saved (updated each time a skill is used). The main attribute deals 165 (+100% of physical attack) physical damage. The sub-attribute deals 49 (+30% of physical attack) physical damage to other nearby enemies.\nWhen the skill is activated, the Blue Sky Dragon acquires 1 stack of Dragon Soul Mark (up to 3 stacks). After acquiring the engraving, the next normal attack will consume all engravings and attack the target with the dragon soul. The number of attacks increases by 1 for each stack of engraving consumed. This enhanced normal attack has different effects depending on the current main attribute.\nWhen performing additional attacks using the Dragon Soul Seal, the second and subsequent attacks will only deal 50% damage. When switching attributes, the same attributes are preferentially retained.",
      "tags": [
