      "description": "Releases sword energy, dealing 300 (300 + 60% of additional physical attack) physical damage and 75 (75 + 15% of additional physical attack) true damage (+50% splash damage to the rear of the target) to up to 3 targets within range. Additionally, obtain 1 stack of Dragon Soul Seal.\nWhen you activate \"Twilight Palm Flame\", you will gain 1 stack of fire attribute and add 15 physical damage to your normal attacks. The following effects will be exerted depending on the currently saved attributes.\nBoth main and sub are fire attributes: Damage increases by an additional 50%.\nMain attribute is fire: The first attack of the enhanced normal attack deals 103 (54 + 30% of physical attack) true damage, and the next two attacks deal 103 (54 + 30% of physical attack) physical damage.",
