      "description": "Releases sword energy, dealing 240 (240 + 35% of additional physical attack) physical damage (+50% splash damage to the rear of the target) to up to 3 targets within range. If hit, recovers 150 (150 + 2.5% of additional maximum HP) HP.\nWhen you activate \"Blue Sky Rain\", you will gain 1 stack of water attributes and recover 18 HP and 0.5% of maximum MP with normal attacks.\nAcquires the following effects depending on the currently saved attributes.\n・Both main and sub are water attributes: Recovery effect increases by an additional 50%.\n・Main attribute is water: Enhanced Normal attack deals 103 (54 + 30% of physical attack) physical damage 3 times, and when the attack hits, recovers 150 HP (150 + 2.5% of additional maximum HP).\nIf the skill hits a non-hero unit, the healing effect will be 20%. If a normal attack hits a non-hero unit, the healing effect is reduced to 50%.",
