      "description": "Releases sword energy, dealing 240 (240 + 35% of additional physical attack) physical damage (+50% splash damage to the back of the target) to up to 3 targets within range, and knocking them back. Also, own movement speed increases by 30% (decreases continuously).\nWhen you activate ``Slash Slash'', you will gain 1 stack of wind attributes and increase your movement speed by 16.\nAcquires the following effects depending on the currently saved attributes.\n・Both main and sub attributes are wind attributes: Movement speed is additionally increased by 50%.\n・Main attribute is wind attribute: Deals 103 (54 + 30% of physical attack) physical damage and knocks back 3 times when using a strengthened normal attack.",
