    "skill4": {
      "name": "Skill 4: Infinite Vastness",
      "description": "Soars into the sky as a dragon for up to 4.5 seconds. During this time, you will be unable to attack, ignore the terrain, and become unable to target (can be interrupted by tapping again). After that, it swoops forward (untargetable), deals 400 (400 + 80% of additional physical attack) physical damage to enemies along the route, reduces movement speed by 15%, deals the same damage again to enemies at the landing point, and applies the Scary Dragon effect for 1 second.\nAfter that, attack speed increases by 20% and range increases by 50 for 10 seconds, and attacks with Shinryuken. During this time, additional damage will be dealt to up to 2 nearby targets using 2 attributes.\nTargets given the Scary Dragon effect will automatically move away from the Blue Sky Dragon. During flight, you can freely change the attributes currently held.",
