    "passive": {
      "name": "Parting Moon",
      "description": "Holds 3 moon rings. Casting \"Swift Foot\" or \"Flowing Light\" consumes 1 moon ring. When all moon rings are consumed, the next basic attack is enhanced, and \"Swift Foot\" and \"Flowing Light\" enter normal cooldowns. The enhanced basic attack generates 3 orbs, each dealing 50 (+10% Magical Attack) magical damage. When \"Swift Foot\" and \"Flowing Light\" hit, they apply 1 stack of mark to the target. Hitting them again triggers a different effect.",
      "table": {
        "headers": [
          "Lv.1",
          "Lv.15"
        ],
        "rows": [
          {
