    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Can isolate key targets with her ultimate, forcing a 1v1 battle.",
        "Stable poke from long range and self-sustain through her passive.",
        "High burst damage from chaining skills by consuming moon energy."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Very squishy if hit by burst damage before casting her ultimate.",
        "Impact decreases against enemies with anti-heal items or high magical defense.",
        "Struggles to escape if forced into close combat or targeted by highly mobile assassins."
      ],
      "playstyle": "In the early game, use skills from a safe distance to clear waves and create advantages through vision and zoning. In team fights, her primary role is to land her ultimate on the enemy's most troublesome carry or support, dragging them into another dimension and forcing a 4v4 situation. Inside the isolated space, secure the 1v1 by chaining skills and utilizing passive damage."
    }
  },
