      "weaknesses": [
        "Complex gauge management and skill sequencing; execution errors can be fatal.",
        "Low inherent durability is easily exposed when locked down by crowd control.",
        "If he fails to secure an early advantage, it's hard to make an impact in late-game team fights."
      ],
      "playstyle": "Always be mindful of your Star Power (passive gauge). The fundamental strategy is to enter combat with 1 or 2 bars filled, allowing you to chain enhanced skills. Capitalize on high mobility to clear the jungle quickly, then consistently employ hit-and-run tactics to ambush isolated enemies or backline carries. When taking heavy fire, use the ultimate to negate damage and outlast opponents."
    }
  },
