        "Distinct passive that scales her skill damage the further away she is from the target.",
        "Ultimate provides instant skill cooldown resets and chained control effects."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Lacks any mobility skills, making it very difficult to escape once enemies close the gap.",
        "Requires predicting enemy movements to land skills, demanding high mechanical skill.",
        "Often lacks the burst damage to secure kills alone, making teamwork essential."
      ],
      "playstyle": "Keep your distance to maximize the bonus damage from your passive, poking and zoning enemies from safety. In team fights, your primary job is to mark a key enemy target and use your ultimate combo to forcibly drag them into your team's formation. Given your low self-peel, avoid venturing out alone and always position yourself where teammates can support you."
    }
  },
