      "cooldown": "CD: 10s",
      "description": "Meng Ya fires a heavy round in a target direction, dealing 200 (+50% extra Physical Attack) physical damage to enemies hit and slowing them by 25% for 2s. Upon hitting an enemy, a wall, or reaching max range, it explodes into 5 splinters. Splinters bounce off walls, dealing 410 (+100% extra Physical Attack) physical damage to the first enemy hit.\nExcited State: The number of splinters increases from 5 to 9.\nHitting enemies with the heavy round or splinters grants 5 Anger. If multiple splinters hit the same target within 1s, the damage is reduced to 25%.",
      "table": {
        "headers": [
