      "cooldown": "CD: 6s",
      "description": "Slashes enemies twice, dealing 225 (+45% extra Physical Attack) physical damage per hit. Each cast grants 1 mark, and additional marks are gained for each enemy hit (cannot gain multiple marks from the same enemy. Max 3 marks). Hitting enemies heals him for 85 (+15% extra Physical Attack + 1% extra Max HP) HP (halved for non-hero units).\nWhen marks are stacked, basic attacks consume 1 mark to become enhanced. Enhanced basic attacks cause him to dash to the enemy, dealing 177 (50 + 75% Physical Attack) physical damage and healing for 85 (+15% extra Physical Attack + 1% extra Max HP) HP. Each follow-up attack reduces the cooldown of Space Split by 10% - 20%.\nCasting Space Split while submerged makes him dash in a target direction and reduces the CD of Wavebreaker by 25%.",
