      "name": "Death From Below",
      "tags": [
        "Crowd Control",
        "Damage",
        "Movement"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD: 40s",
      "description": "Throws a dagger in a target direction, drastically slowing enemies along the path for 0.5s. After a short delay, he dashes to the dagger's location, dealing 520 (+180% extra Physical Attack) physical damage to enemies along the path and pulling them to the dagger's destination.\nIf submerged, he pulls enemies along the path to the end of the dash and reduces the CD of Wavebreaker by 50%.",
      "table": {
        "headers": [
