              "60"
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "Has overwhelming mobility and evasion ability by dashing and switching positions.",
        "By resetting skills using passives, you can create instantaneous and continuous burst damage."
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "Skill operation is very complex and requires high player skill and practice",
        "Weak against CC, and if you can't lead by gold difference, your presence in the middle and later stages tends to fade."
      ],
      "playstyle": "A powerful combo that resets the skill by hitting the mirror image and the main body attack at the same time, causing constant damage. During ultimate deployment, the positions of the main body and mirror image can be swapped instantly, allowing you to attack unilaterally while avoiding enemy attacks. In group battles, be aware of hit and away, where you wait for an ally to initiate, assassinate an enemy with low health or a soft backline hero with a reliable burst combo, and immediately leave."
    },
    "meta": {
      "summoner_spells": [
        "Smite"
      ],
      "synergy": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Lady Zhen",
          "reason": "This is because it stops the enemy's movement with a wide range of CC and creates a perfect starting point for skill combos.",
          "hero_id": "hero_028"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Mai Shiranui",
          "reason": "Both have high mobility and burst damage, allowing them to quickly annihilate the enemy's backline.",
          "hero_id": "hero_050"
        }
      ],
      "counters": [
        {
          "hero_name": "Ata",
          "reason": "This is because they have extremely high durability and CC, and their skill combos and movements are blocked and they cannot get kills.",
          "hero_id": "hero_107"
        },
        {
          "hero_name": "Daji",
          "reason": "Due to the targeted stun and overwhelming burst damage, there is a high risk of being defeated before you can get close.",
          "hero_id": "hero_008"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
