      "cooldown": "CD: 18 seconds",
      "description": "Starting technique: Draws 7 sword marks on the spot and attacks nearby enemies up to 3 times, dealing 320 (320 + 75% of additional physical attack) physical damage each time and reducing movement speed by 25% for 1 second. While the skill is active, you will gain super armor status and a passive effect that reduces damage taken.\nIf you damage an enemy multiple times, the damage from the second time onwards will be reduced to 30%.",
      "icon": "/images/skills/hero_102_skill3.png",
      "forms": [
        {
          "form_name": "usually",
          "description": "Starting technique: Draws 7 sword marks on the spot and attacks nearby enemies up to 3 times, dealing 320 (320 + 75% of additional physical attack) physical damage each time and reducing movement speed by 25% for 1 second. While the skill is active, you will gain super armor status and a passive effect that reduces damage taken.\nIf you damage an enemy multiple times, the damage from the second time onwards will be reduced to 30%.",
          "table": null
        },
        {
          "form_name": "After switching",
          "description": "Additional technique: Quickly draws 7 sword marks on the spot (skill activation speed is faster than the starting technique), attacks nearby enemies up to 3 times, deals 320 (320 + 75% of physical attack) physical damage each time, and reduces movement speed by 25% for 1 second.\nIf you damage an enemy multiple times, the damage from the second time onwards will be reduced to 30%.\nAfter completing the sword formation, activate \"Power Gradation\" and deal the same amount of damage again to the enemy in the center of the sword mark, knocking them up for 0.75 seconds. While the skill is active, you will gain super armor status and a passive effect that reduces damage taken.",
          "table": {
            "headers": [
