          "form_name": "usually",
          "description": "Raise your spear, charge and charge (maximum movement speed increased by 25%). After charging, charge forward and mow down the enemy, dealing 180 (180 + 60% of additional physical attack) to 360 (360 + 120% of additional physical attack) physical damage and reducing movement speed by 15% for 1 second.",
          "table": null
        },
        {
          "form_name": "Resonance・2 stacks: Eagerness・Castle Destruction",
          "description": "Performs three consecutive attacks. The first two attacks each deal 129 (60 + 40% of physical attack) physical damage to the enemy and restore 90 HP (90 + 1.3% of additional HP). The final attack deals 258 (120 + 80% of physical attack) physical damage and restores 180 HP (180 + 2.5% of additional HP).\nActivates with normal attack when resonance stacks 2. The lower the HP, the more the recovery amount will be (up to 2x).",
