        "CC",
        "super armor"
      ],
      "cooldown": "CD: 40 seconds",
      "description": "Fills the tip of the spear with flame and moves it back and forth towards the front area, dealing 180 (180 + 60% of additional physical attack) physical damage each time and knocking it up.\nWhen the maximum distance is reached, it will pierce continuously, dealing 90 (90 + 30% of additional physical attack) physical damage each time (4 times in total).\nWhile the skill is active, you will be in a super armor state, reducing damage taken by 30%, and can activate the second stage skill \"Roar of Spears\" which mowing down and burning the front.\nScrape deals 180 (180 + 60% of additional physical attack) physical damage, and Burn Area deals 50 (50 + 16% of additional physical attack) magic damage once every 0.2 seconds for 3 seconds.\nThe second stage can be activated while \"Tracing Star\" is activated. Mows down the surrounding area, cancels the subsequent charge, deals 120 (120 + 40% of additional physical attack) physical damage, and burns a circular area for 3 seconds.",
