    "status_text": "Basic status\nMax HP: 3335\nMax MP: 560\nPhysical attack: 185 (175+10)\nMagic attack: 0\nPhysical Defense: 150|20%\nMagic Defense: 75|11.1%\n\nattack status\nMovement speed: 380\nPhysical defense penetration: 0|0%\nMagic defense penetration: 0|0%\nAttack speed bonus: 5%\nCritical rate: 0%\nCritical effect: 200%\nPhysical Lifesteal: 0%\nMagic life steal: 0%\nCooldown reduction: 0%\nAttack range: close range\n\ndefense status\nResistance: 0%\nHP recovery every 5 seconds: 48\nMP recovery every 5 seconds: 14",
    "strategy": {
      "strengths": [
        "A unique passive that allows you to move on walls allows you to surprise attack from unpredictable routes.",
        "Do not miss low HP enemies with the powerful slashing (certain killing) ability of the ultimate \"Jade\""
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "If you are thrown off a wall or CC'd, you will be extremely vulnerable and will have no means of escape.",
        "The difficulty of operation is high, and it is difficult to demonstrate your strengths in places where you cannot use walls to move around."
      ],
      "playstyle": "A high-mobility Assassin that flies freely over walls and quickly closes the distance from the enemy's line of sight to assassinate soft rearguards. Skill 2 allows you to climb walls to gain movement and visibility, and skill 1 allows you to charge at enemies and knock them up. After dealing damage, if the enemy's health drops below a certain line (1/8), you can activate the ultimate slashing effect to ensure a final blow. During an engagement, it is important to always be aware of the escape wall."
    },
